            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikushaba, kandi eego,nintura n'ab'omuka yangye, nahabwekyo nitugamba aha bintu bitari bimwe na bimwe.",
            "Ngaaha, tinkahikirweho obusaasi obutarikwetegyerezibwa obwahati. Ntwire ninyehurira gye.",
            "Eego,ndeebire okuzimba omu mikono n'ebigyere byangye.",
            "Eego, nitubaasa kutunga obutimba bw'ensiri, obu turikukoresa kwerinda omushwija gw'ensiri.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kutaayaayira banywani bangye.",
            "Eego, mbaasize kuhuumura kurungi, kandi nyine obuhwezi omuka.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kurya emirundi eshatu buri eizooba.",
            " Tindikuhurira gye okuzaara obwahati ahabwokuba omwana wangye ondiijo ni muto, kandi nintiina kureeberera bombi.",
            " Eego, ntwire nimpurira nyine oburemeezi n'okwerarikirira ahabw'okuba ntwire enda obu omwana wangye owa kabiri akiri muto munonga.",
