            "Eego,ninkoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa nka ekyoganyanja.",
            "Omu mirimo yangye eya burizooba harimu okuhinga n'okukora emirimo y'omuka. Ninshanga okuhinga nikutwara amaani maingi.",
            "Eego, nitubaasa kutunga amaizi marungi g'okunywa n'okuteeka.",
            "Kuruga obu naabaire nyine enda y'ahamuheru, n'einyine hati, ndweire omushwija gw'ensiri, okikorora hamwe na senyiga.",
            "Ngaaha, tinkatunga burwaire obutarikukira ninga embeera yoona  erikubaasa kurabanisamu enda yangye.",
            "Ngaaha, tihaine byafaayo by'oburemeezi bw'enzaarwa oburikumanywa omu kika gangye.",
            "Ninkira kurya ebyokurya nka ebitooke, akahunga, omuceeri, hamwe n'emboga, kandi eego, ninyikiriza ngu nimbaasa kurinda ebyokurya ebirimu ebiriisa byona.",
            "Ninkoresa obwire bwangye kukora, kwonka nyine obwire bw'okubyama n'okuhuumura.",
            "Nimbaasa gye oburemeezi obwo ndikugamba na mazaara, omuntu ou ndikubaasa kugamba nawe ebindi aha mutima.",
