            "Ndebire ngu ku ndikutambura kumara obwire bureingwa amaguru gangye nigashaasha kandi gazimba.",
            "Eego, nitubaasa kutunga obutimba bw'ensiri, obu turikukoresa kwerinda omushwija gw'ensiri.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kuhurikiriza reediyo nainga okugamba n'abagyenyi.",
