            "Mpulira bulungi okubeera maama, kiba kirungi, era mu kiseera kino, sirina kye nneeraliikirira kitongole ekikwatagana n‚Äôomulimu gwange ng‚Äôomuzadde omupya. Olugendo luno ndunyumirwa nnyo.",
