            "Nedda, sigoberera nkola oba nzikiriza yonna ey‚Äôobuwangwa entongole. Okutwalira awamu bye nsalawo n‚Äôebikolwa byange byesigamiziddwa ku kutegeera kwange n‚Äôokumanya okwa bulijjo.",
            "Yee nfuna obulumi okuva ku nkovu we nnalongosebwa nga nzaala. Obutabeera bulungi buno kintu kye ndabilira ng‚Äôekimu ku bigenda okuwona oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala era nnina essuubi nti kijja kutereera mpolampola ng‚Äôekiwundu kigenda kiwona okumala ekiseera.",
            "Nyonsa omwana wange emirundi nga kkumi n‚Äôebiri olunaku era kirabika okutwalira awamu omwana aba mumativu oluvannyuma lwa buli kiseera ky‚Äôokumuyonsa kano kabonero akalungi eri endya ye n‚Äôamabeele gange.",
            "Yee ndabye enkyukakyuka mu ngeri omwana wange gy‚Äôalya; naddala omwana abadde asesema oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuyonka. Kino kye nneeraliikiridde era nteekateeka okunoonya abasawo amagezi okutegeera kwe kiva.",
