            "Olw‚Äôokusanyuka, nnyumirwa nnyo okutambulatambula okugenda okukyalira mikwano gyange buli lwe kiba kisoboka. Okugatta ku ekyo, omwami wange oluusi antwala mu bifo ebisanyukiddwamu, era eno y‚Äôengeri ennungi gye nnyinza okuwummulamu n‚Äôokunyumirwa akaseera nga ndi wabweru w‚Äôawaka.",
