            "Nedda, sirina kibuuzo kyonna kitongole oba ekinneeraliikiriza ku bulamu bwange mu kiseera kino. Essira nditadde ku kudda engulu n‚Äôokulaba ng‚Äôomwana wange mulamu bulungi era ng‚Äôalabirirwa bulungi.",
