            "1. okukyusa paadi z‚Äôomwana buli kiseera 2. Okunaaba mu ngalo buli kiseera 3. Okulya emmere ennungi 4. Okunaaba buli kiseera 4. Okwambala engoye ennyonjo",
            "Nga nzuula mikwano gyange n‚Äôab‚Äôomu maka ge beesigika be njogera nabo ku kusoomoozebwa kwange buli kiseera.",
            "Gabana n‚Äôemikwano n‚Äôab‚Äôomu maka ge beesigika, yingiza bannange mu bikwata ku baana, genda mu ddwaaliro ly‚Äôebyobulamu eriri okumpi",
            "Nga nfuna ekiwummulo ekimala, okugenda okwekebejjebwa abasawo buli kiseera, nga nneebikka ekimala",
            "Yee. Nze nkuwa amagezi okukola dduyiro wa kegel, n'okwenyiga n'amazzi aga bbuguma.",
            "Nze nandironze emmere ey‚Äôebbeeyi entono. Era nnandikozesezza olusuku lwange olw‚Äôemabega w'enyumba",
            "1. Okubeera n‚Äôobulumi bungi 2. Puleesa okweyongera 3. Amazzi agawunya obubi okuva mubukyala 4. omusujja n‚Äôokuziyira",
            "Bw‚Äôoba tosobola kugenda mu kifo eky‚Äôebyobulamu olw‚Äôobutabeera bulungi oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala wano mu Uganda era nga tolina bukakafu ku ngeri gy‚Äôoyinza okubukakanyaamu, kiyinza okuba eky‚Äôomugaso okunoonya amagezi okuva mu bantu beesigika, gamba ng‚Äôabakadde oba bammemba ba Village Health Team, abayinza okuba nga balina okumanya ku ddagala eritali lya bulabe eri awaka. Bwe kiba kisoboka, gezaako okutuukirira omusawo w‚Äôebyobulamu ku ssimu akuwe obulagirizi.",
            "Yee; Okukola dduyiro, Okunywa amazzi agabuguma, Okutambula",
            "Okutegeeza ab'omu maka ag'okumpi, aba VHT, n'abakulembeze b'omu kitundu abayinza okukuyamba okufuna obujjanjabi.",
            "Waliwo enkozesa ye eddagala ly'einnansi okwanguya enkola y‚Äôokuzaala",
            "Nze ku lwange sirina kye ngoberera, naye mpulidde emikwano egikkiririza mu kukakasa nti omwana atuumibwa erinnya lya bajjajja ba kitaawe",
            "Mpulira bulungi okubeera maama. Ebisinga okunneeraliikiriza kwe kuteebaka biseera by'ekilo olw‚Äôomwana okukaaba bulijjo. Kino kikosezza nnyo obulamu bwange obw'obwongo.",
            "Nedda, sirina kibuuzo kyonna oba kweraliikirira ku bulamu bwange for sure mu kiseera kino. Mpulira bulungi era essira nditadde ku kudda engulu n‚Äôokulabirira omwana wano mu Uganda.",
            "Njagala nnyo okuzannya SODUKU ku ssimu yange. Nze era ndaba nnyo obutambi bwa TIKTOK",
            "Yee, bulijjo njogera ne munnange. Ku ky‚Äôokukkakkanya situleesi, nkola ebintu ebimp'essanyu ng‚Äôokuzannya puzzle ku ssimu ate n‚Äôokulaba obutambi bwa TIKTOK",
            "Yee, okwenyiga n'amazzi agabuguma, okunaaza omwana wange mu ddagala ly'ekinnansi limmannyiddwa nga kyogero",
            "Yee, nfunye. Mpulira bulungi nnyo kubanga mazima ddala kizzaamu amaanyi era kimatiza",
            "Mubutufu nedda, Sirina kibuuzo kyonna kitongole oba ekinneeraliikiriza ku bulamu bwange mu kiseera kino. Essira nditadde ku kudda engulu oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala n‚Äôobulamu obulungi bw‚Äôomwana wange, oboolyawo omusawo ow'omu maaso.",
            "Mpulira kinene nnyo ku mubiri gwange. Okudda engulu ddala kugenda mu maaso bulungi.",
            "Nga omira amazzi amangi okuddamu amazzi, ng‚Äôokozesa ‚Äòwarm compress‚Äô emirundi 3 olunaku okumalawo obulumi",
            "Nnali ntunuulidde ekifo ky‚Äôebyobulamu ekisinga okumpi ne nnoonya obujjanjabi obwetaagisa okuva eri omusawo omukugu mu by‚Äôobulamu. Nze era nandyebuuzizza ku yintaneeti",
            "Kozesa amazzi agabuguma n‚Äôomunnyo okunaaba ekiwundu okwetooloola emisono. Era si kibi okunaaba n‚Äôomunnyo",
            "Obubonero mulimu: Obulumi n‚Äôobutabeera bulungi, omusujja, okuwunya obubi okuva mu masira n‚Äôomusaayi. Engeri y‚Äôokwetangira: Kuuma obuyonjo obulungi, endya ennungi, dduyiro n‚Äôokumira eddagala eriragiddwa",
            "1. Nga okola emirimu emitono, bwe kiba kisoboka, ng‚Äôotudde. 2. Okumira eddagala eriweweeza ku bulumi 3. Lya emmere ennungi",
            "Nze nanditegeezezza ab'enganda ab'oku lusegere, nenkozesa paadi.. Era singa okuvaamu omusaayi kussuka, bwe kiba nti nkozesa paadi  3 mu ssaawa emu oba wansi we ssaawa, awo nga nenda u ddwaliro eriri kumpi amangu ddala.",
            "Kebera omusaayi ng‚Äôowekaanya ku muwendo gwa paadi. Tezilina kusukka 3 mu lunaku. Kebera oba obbulumi bweyogera, olwo loopa mu ddwaaliro erikuli okumpi.",
            "Yee. Okuwa nakawere emmere elimu ebirungo ebizimba omubiri ebimala, enva endiirwa ne ssupu. Kuno kw‚Äôogatta omuceere, ennyama, ssukaali. Enkola endala mulimu okwenyigga ng‚Äôokozesa endaggala ezibuguma.",
            "Maama akubirizibwa okulya emmere eyokya nga erimu ssupu amala n‚Äôekikopo ky‚Äôekibugumu nga kirimu ssukaali buli lw‚Äôamaze okulya emirundi 3 olunaku",
            "Nga oyonsa buli kiseera, okukola dduyiro, okukendeeza ku ssukaali gw‚Äôonywa, okwenyigira mu mirimu gy‚Äôawaka, okussa ekkomo ku mmere erimu amasavu n‚Äôekisembayo, okulya emmere etali yakabohaidureti.",
            "Nga okyusa paadi oba obutawulo buli kiseera, okusala enviiri z‚Äôomu bitundu by'ekyaama buli wiiki, okwoza engoye buli kiseera, n‚Äôokunaaba waakiri emirundi 2 olunaku.",
            "Okulya obulungi n‚Äôokunywa amazzi amangi, okuwummula ekimala, bw‚Äôoba n‚Äôobulumi, mmira eddagala eriragiddwa. Singa obubonero busigala nga bukyaliwo, nsaba oloope mu ddwaaliro eriri okumpi.",
            "Tuukirira mukwano gwo oba ow‚Äôoluganda lw‚Äôoku lusegere, genda ew‚Äôomubuulirizi, noonya obuyambi okukola ebifo by‚Äôeddiini ng‚Äôamakanisa, genda mu kifo ky‚Äôebyobulamu ekikuriraanye.",
            "Bw‚Äôonnywa amazzi mangi olw'okuddamu amazzi, funa ekiwummulo ekiwanvu, mmira eddagala eriweweeza ku bulumi, okwebikka ekimala ng'olimu bulili. Singa obubonero obwo busigalawo, genda mu ddwaaliro erikuriraanye.",
            "Yee, dduyiro w‚Äôomu bitundu by'esambi nga okusittama, okukwata omusulo ng‚Äôofuka omusulo nga toguleka kukulukuta mangu.",
            "Nga olya emmere erimu ekiriisa ekizimba omubiri (Ebijanjaalo, ebinyeebwa, soya), ebimera nga kasooli oba emmere nga obumonde, lumonde oba amatooke",
            "Okuvaamu omusaayi omungi ekiyinza okweyoleka ng‚Äôokyusa paadi ezisukka mu 3 buli lunaku, okulumwa olubuto olwa wansi, omusujja n‚Äôokuziyira, okulumwa omusaayi, okusesema n‚Äôokusiiyibwa, okulaba obubi oba obutalaba bulungi, okuvaamu amazzi agawunya obubi.",
            "Bw‚Äôonywa ebyokunywa ebibuguma, okunyiga olubuto mu ng'ozesa endagala n‚Äôokumira obusera ng‚Äôomaze okuggyamu.",
            "Yee: 1. emmere ey‚Äôekinnansi etegekeddwa obulungi ng‚Äôeriibwa eyokya oba ennyogovu 2. emmere ofumbiddwa era nennyigiddwa mu ndagala 3. Okunywa obusera ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala",
            "Ntegeeza ab‚Äôenganda, abakulembeze ba VHT ab‚Äôomukitundu, abakulembeze b‚Äôekkanisa era bwe kiba kisoboka, ntegeeza oba nkubira omukozi w‚Äôebyobulamu essimu.",
            "Okukozesa eddagala ly'ekinnansi nga ndinaaba, okulilya oba okulinywa.",
            "Nedda, sigoberera nnyo nkola oba nzikiriza yonna ey‚Äôobuwangwa entongole. Enkola yange etera kwesigama nnyo ku bye njagala ku bwange n‚Äôokumanya okwawamu okusinga okunywerera ku nnono z‚Äôobuwangwa ezenjawulo wano mu Uganda.",
            " Mpulira bulungi nnyo okubeera maama; kinyuma nnyo wano mu Uganda. Wabula ekisinga okuntiisa kwe kulowooza ku kufiirwa omwana ng‚Äôamaze okuzaala, ekintu ekinneeraliikiriza ennyo.",
            " Nedda, sirina kibuuzo kyonna kitongole oba ekinneeraliikiriza ku bulamu bwange mu kiseera kino wano mu Uganda. Essira nditadde ku mbeera yange ennungi n‚Äôokulabirira omwana wange era mpulira ng‚Äôebintu bigenda bulungi.",
            " Yee, ddala nnina obudde obw‚Äôokuwummulamu wano mu Uganda, era okusanyuka, nnyumirwa nnyo okulaba obuzannyo bwa ttivvi, okubeela ku TikTok, okwogera ne mikwano gyange, era n‚Äôokwenyigira mu dduyiro w‚Äôomubiri okusobola okusigala nga ndi munyikivu era nga nsanyuka.",
            "Nzikakanya situleesi nga mpita mu bintu byanjawulo wano mu Uganda, omuli okuwuliriza ennyimba z‚Äôeggwanga, okulaba ttivvi, okwogera ne mikwano gyange okumpa obuyambi, n‚Äôokwenyigira mu kukola dduyiro ebiyamba okulongoosa ebirowoozo byange n‚Äôokuwulira obulungi.",
            " Yee, enkola ey‚Äôekinnansi gye nkozesa wano mu Uganda y‚Äôengeri ey‚Äôokuteekateeka emmere, gamba ng‚Äôokufumbira amatooke mu ndagala okugaboobeza. Eno nkola ya bulijjo mu buwangwa bwaffe era nsiima obuwoomi n‚Äôenkola.",
            " Yee, nsobodde okukwatagana n‚Äôomwana wange wano mu Uganda, era mpulira bulungi nnyo naddala mu kiseera ky‚Äôokuyonsa. Ebiseera ebyo eby‚Äôokusemberera bireeta akakwate ak‚Äôamaanyi wakati waffe, kye nsinga okwagala.",
            " Nedda, sirina kyenbuuza wadde okweraliikirira ku bulamu bwange mu kiseera kino wano mu Uganda. Mpulira bulungi era essira nditadde ku kudda engulu n‚Äôobulamu obulungi bw‚Äôomwana wange.",
            "1. Njagala nnyo omubiri gwange 2. Nguliisa ku mmere ennungi nga ku puloteyina n‚Äôenva endiirwa 3. Nkuuma obuyonjo obulungi nga okunaaba buli kiseera, okwoza engoye buli kiseera 4. Nfuna otulo otumala 5. Nkola dduyiro oluusi",
            "Nyiga n'amazzi agabuguma, okufuna ekiwummulo ekimala, okunywa amazzi agabuguma",
            "Bw‚Äôonaaba ekiwundu n‚Äôamazzi ag‚Äôomunnyo agabuguma, kyoze ne ssabbuuni ow‚Äôokwooza. Era obubonero bwe busigala nga bukyaliwo, loopa mu ddwaaliro erikuli okumpi.",
            "Ziyonje n‚Äôamazzi amayonjo agafumbiddwa ag‚Äôomunnyo, kyusa paadi emirundi 3-4 olunaku",
            "Obubonero: Omusujja n‚Äôokuziyira, obulumi mu lubuto, amazzi agawunya mu ngeri etaali ya bulijjo, obutayagala mmere, okulabika ng‚Äôoli mulwadde.",
            "Tuukirira ab‚Äôenganda mpozzi osabe okusulayo, gezaako okukola ng‚Äôotudde, fuga obulumi, okulya obulungi okufuna amaanyi, tondawo obudde bw‚Äôokuwummula",
            "Kola dduyiro enyangu, nywa eddagala eriragiddwa, nywa amazzi mangi",
            "Kuba olubuto okukebera oba sayizi ekendeera, kebera oba omusaayi gukendeera ng‚Äôolondoola omuwendo gwa paadi ezeetaagisa buli lunaku",
            "Yee: Amazzi agabuguma agalimu omunnyo, ganyigiriza n‚Äôamazzi agabuguma ng‚Äôokozesa endagala.",
            "Ddira ekikopo ky‚Äôobuuji obutabuddwamu soya w‚Äôamata (nnya) oba emmere ey‚Äôempeke yonna buli luvannyuma lwa ssaawa 4. Wenyigge n'amazzi  n'ebikoola by‚Äôebijanjaalo nga bibbuguma.",
            "Nga olina emmere elimu ebiriisa byonna, okukola dduyiro buli kiseera",
            "Nga onaaba buli kiseera, okukyusa paadi buli kiseera, bulijjo naaba mu ngalo nga tonnaba n‚Äôoluvannyuma lw‚Äôokukwata ku mwana.  ",
            "Nga njogera ne mukwano gwange ow‚Äôoku lusegere ku kusoomoozebwa kwe njolekedde, okukwata ebirowoozo byange nga nsoma baibuli, okukuba ennyimba z‚Äôenjiri",
            "Nga ogenda mu ddwaaliro mu bwangu",
            "Nga omira eddagala eriweweeza ku bulumi nga paracentamol, n‚Äôokuwuumula ekimala.",
            "Yee, dduyiro wa Kegel asengekeddwa nnyo okuwona oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala era nga kyangu okukolebwa awaka wano mu Uganda. Dduyiro ono ayamba okunyweza ebinywa by‚Äôomu kifuba ebiyinza okuba nga byagololwa ng‚Äôozaala. (ebigambo 33)",
            "Okukakasa endya entuufu okusobola okudda engulu ng‚Äôemmere entono wano mu Uganda, kikulu okukozesa emmere eriwo mu ngeri ekwatagana n‚Äôebiriisa, nga tukulembeza ebirungo ebizimba omubiri, ebirungo ebizimba omubiri, n‚Äôebibala oba enva endiirwa zonna eziriwo. (ebigambo 33)",
            "Obubonero obulaga nti weetaaga okugenda mu ddwaaliro mu bwangu ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala wano mu Uganda mulimu okuvaamu omusaayi omungi nga gulimu n‚Äôebizimba, okuwulira ekiwuubaalo obutasalako, okuwunya n‚Äôomusujja, oba omwana bw‚Äôaba tasobola kuyonka. (ebigambo 34)",
            "Bw‚Äôoba tosobola kugenda mu kifo eky‚Äôebyobulamu mu Uganda, osobola okuddukanya obutabeera bulungi oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala ng‚Äôokola dduyiro mu ngeri ey‚Äôobukkakkamu n‚Äôokwenyigira mu mirimu egisobola okukukuuma ng'lina amaanyi, gamba ng‚Äôokugenda mu pulogulaamu z‚Äôekkanisa oba emikolo emirala egy‚Äôomu kitundu. (ebigambo 37)",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola z‚Äôekinnansi wano mu Uganda eziyinza okuyamba mu kudda engulu oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala, gamba ng‚Äôokunnywa  eddagala ly'ekinnansi ely‚Äôomu kitundu nga emumbwa n‚Äôokukozesa eddagala eribuguma eriweweeza ku mubiri okukkakkanya obuzibu n‚Äôokuyamba okuwona. (ebigambo 31)",
            "Bw‚Äôofuna obuzibu ate nga tolina busobozi kugenda mu ddwaaliro mu Uganda, olw‚Äôokuvaamu omusaayi omungi, gezaako okuyonsa ennyo okuyamba nnabaana okukonziba, ate ku musujja, osobola okumira eddagala eriweweeza ku bulumi nga paracetamol bwe libaawo. (ebigambo 36)",
            "Enzikiriza oba enkola eza bulijjo mu kitundu kyange wano mu Uganda mulimu okunnywa eddagala ly'ekinnansi elimu okugezaako okwanguya okuzaala, era abantu abamu bakkiririza mu kunnywa omwenge ogw‚Äôomu kitundu (waragi) n‚Äôekigendererwa eky‚Äôokuzaala omwana omuyonjo. (ebigambo 35)",
            "Yee, ngoberera enkola z‚Äôobuwangwa oba enzikiriza ezimu wano mu Uganda, gamba ng‚Äôezo ezoogeddwako waggulu ku bikwata ku ddagala ely'ekinnansi ely‚Äôokuzaala n‚Äôenzikiriza ekwata ku mwenge gw‚Äôomu kitundu (waragi) mu kiseera ky'okuzaala, anti bino bimu ku nnono zaffe. (ebigambo 35)",
            "Mazima mpulira nga nneenyumiriza mu kubeera maama wano mu Uganda. Kirabika sirina kinneeraliikiriza mu kiseera kino ku bikwata ku kifo kyange ng‚Äôomuzadde omupya, era nkwatira ddala kino. (ebigambo 31)",
            "Mpozzi, okusinziira ku kuba nti nnina enkovu ttaano ezaaliwo emabega okuva mu kuzaala emabegako wano mu Uganda, ekibuuzo kyange kiri nti oba ddala tekirina bulabe gyendi okuddamu okufuna olubuto mu biseera eby‚Äôomu maaso. Kuno kwe kweraliikiriza kwe nnina. (ebigambo 37)",
            "Ku lw‚Äôokusanyuka wano mu Uganda, nnyumirwa nnyo okumala ebiseera byange nga mpuliriza ennyimba z‚Äôenjiri, ze nsanga nga zizzaamu amaanyi, era n‚Äôokutambulako akawungeezi akawummuza nga nfunye omukisa. (ebigambo 30)",
            "Yee, situleesi mukkakkanya wano mu Uganda nga nkozesa eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi erifumbiddwa okuva mu bimera eby‚Äôomu kitundu. Eno ngeri ya kinnansi gye nnyinza okugumira situleesi, era kintu kye njize mu kitundu kyange. (ebigambo 35)",
            "Yee, nze nkozesa eddagala oba enkola z‚Äôekinnansi wano mu Uganda. Mpulira nga ddala nnenyumiriza era nga ndi musanyufu okuyingiza enkola zino ez‚Äôobuwangwa mu bulamu bwange, kuba kitundu kikulu nnyo mu busika bwaffe era nga zitera okubudaabuda. (ebigambo 36)",
            "Nsobodde okukwatagana ne bbebi wange wano mu Uganda, era mpulira bulungi nnyo. Kyokka, ebinneeraliikiriza ebigenda mu maaso bikwatagana n‚Äôenkovu ttaano ze nnalina emabega n‚Äôengeri gye ziyinza okukosaamu embuto ez‚Äôomu maaso. (ebigambo 39)",
            "Mpulira nga nnenyumiriza mu bulamu bwange wano mu Uganda. Nze nneerabirira nga nkakasa nti nneenyigira mu kunaaba bulijjo olw‚Äôobuyonjo, nga ngezaako okuba n‚Äôemmere ennungi n‚Äôemmere eriwo, era nga nkola dduyiro buli kiseera bwe kiba kisoboka. (ebigambo 37)",
            "[Tewali kuddamu kuweereddwa mu likoda eyasooka.]",
            "Bw‚Äôoba olina obuzibu mu kuwona okuva mu kulongoosebwa ate nga mu Uganda temuli bikozesebwa mu kitundu, kikulu okukuuma embeera ennyonjo okwetooloola ekifo we batemye n‚Äôokutuukirira omusawo w‚Äôebyobulamu singa ofuna obubonero obw‚Äôamaanyi. (ebigambo 38)",
            "Bw‚Äôoba toli kumpi na ddwaaliro mu Uganda nga weetaaga okulabirira emisono oba amaziga ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala, olina okuyonja mpola ekifo n‚Äôamazzi agabuguma era amayonjo n‚Äôokwewala okukola omulimu gwonna ogw‚Äôomubiri omuzito oguyinza okunyigiriza ebitundu ebiwona. (ebigambo 36)",
            "Obubonero bw‚Äôokukwatibwa obulwadde nga bamaze okuzaala wano mu Uganda mulimu ebbugumu eringi, okulumwa omutwe, n‚Äôokuzimba omubiri. Okwetangira osobola okukikola ng‚Äôomira eddagala lyonna eriweebwa omukozi w‚Äôebyobulamu, okukuuma embeera gy‚Äôobeera nga nnyonjo, n‚Äôokulya emmere ennungi okusobola okuwagira abaserikale b‚Äôomubiri. (ebigambo 46)",
            "Obubonero bw'okukwatibwa obulwadde oluvannyuma lw'okuzaala wano mu Uganda mulimu ebbugumu eringi, okulumwa omutwe n'okuzimba omubiri. Okuziyiza kusobola okutuukibwako nga omira eddagala lyonna erikuweebwa omukozi w'ebyobulamu, okukuuma ebikwetolodde nga biyonjo, n'okulya emmere erimu ebirungo byonna okuyamba abasirikale b'omubiri gwo. (46 ebigambo)",
            "Bw‚Äôoba tosobola kuwummula kimala olw‚Äôobuvunaanyizibwa mu bw‚Äôamaka mu kiseera ky'okuwona mu Uganda, osobola okuddukanya obulungi ng‚Äôokakasa nti onywa amazzi mangi ate ng‚Äôokola emirimu gy‚Äôawaka ng‚Äôotudde okukendeeza ku buzibu ku mubiri gwo. (ebigambo 39)",
            "Bw‚Äôovaamu omusaayi ogubeerezaamu ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala wano mu Uganda, olina okunnywa obuuji n'amazzi agalimu  omunnyo, weewale okwegatta nga tegunnatuuka wiiki mukaaga ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala, n‚Äôoloopa mu ddwaaliro erikuli okumpi singa obubonero buno bubeerezaamu. (ebigambo 37)",
            "Osobola okulondoola enkulaakulana yo ey‚Äôokuwona awaka mu Uganda nga tokebereddwa musawo buli kiseera ng‚Äôolaba omusaayi mu bukyala ng‚Äôoyita mu paadi ezikukebera, okwetegereza oba olina ekizimba kyonna mu bitundu byo ebya wansi, n‚Äôokwewala okwegatta mu wiiki omukaaga ezisooka okusobozesa obukyala ne nnabaana okuwona. (ebigambo 45)",
            "Yee, waliwo eddagala oba enkola z‚Äôomu kitundu eziyinza okuyamba okuwona oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala wano mu Uganda, gamba ng‚Äôokukola dduyiro wa Kegel nga weegezaamu okukwata omusulo ng‚Äôofulumya omusulo, n‚Äôokunaaba entabirotabiro nga okozesa omunnyo n‚Äôamazzi agabuguma okukkakkanya obulumi. (ebigambo 40)",
            "Bw‚Äôoba olina obuzibu mu kuyonsa ate nga tolina buyambi bwa kuyonsa mu Uganda, olina okuloopa eri omukozi w‚Äôebyobulamu akuli okumpi naddala ng‚Äôamabeere gazimba oba obubonero obulala bwonna obukwata ku kuyonsa. (ebigambo 34)",
            "Okukwata enkyukakyuka mu buzito oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala ng‚Äôabasawo bakuwa amagezi matono mu Uganda kizingiramu okutegeera nti emirundi mingi kiva ku nkyukakyuka mu mubiri. Okugejja, okukola dduyiro mu ngeri ey‚Äôobwegendereza, okulya emmere ennungi ng‚Äôolina ebirungo ebitono ebiyitibwa kabohaidureti, n‚Äôamazzi amayonjo biyinza okuyamba. Okugejja, essira lisse ku mmere ennungi, otulo otumala, n‚Äôokunoonya obuyambi okusobola okukakanya situleesi. (ebigambo 58)",
            "Enkola ezisinga obulungi ez‚Äôokukuuma obuyonjo bw‚Äôomuntu ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala mu Uganda mulimu okukyusa paadi buli kiseera, okukozesa engoye za ppamba naddala ez‚Äôomunda, okunaaba ennyo, okusinga emirundi ebiri olunaku, okukozesa ssabbuuni okwoza engoye, n‚Äôokukuuma omwana nga muyonjo bulijjo okutangira endwadde. (ebigambo 37)",
            "Bw‚Äôoba owulira ng‚Äôozitoowereddwa era nga tosobola kutuuka ku mubuulirizi ku nsonga z‚Äôobwongo mu Uganda, gezaako okwogera n‚Äôomuntu gwe weesiga, gamba ng‚Äôomuntu ow‚Äôomu maka oba mukwano gwo ow‚Äôoku lusegere, era okkirize okwogera ebikweraliikiriza n‚Äôenneewulira zo mu lwatu. (ebigambo 36)",
            "Bw‚Äôofuna okweraliikirira oba situleesi ey‚Äôamaanyi oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mu Uganda, kikulu okunoonya obuyambi bw‚Äôeby‚Äôomwoyo okuva eri omubuulirizi oba omukozi w‚Äôebyobulamu amangu ddala nga bwe kisoboka, kubanga basobola okukuwa obulagirizi n‚Äôokulabirira okwetaagisa. (ebigambo 34)",
            "Okusobola okukakanya obubonero obutera okulabika oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala ng‚Äôokutuuyana n‚Äôobunyogovu ekiro mu Uganda, kirungi okwewala okunywa ebyokunywa ebyokya n‚Äôokwambala engoye za ppamba, kuba zino zisobola okuyamba okutereeza ebbugumu ly‚Äôomubiri gwo n‚Äôokutereeza obuweerero. (ebigambo 34)",
            "Yee, waliwo dduyiro ez'enjawulo ezisemba okuwona oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala z‚Äôosobola okukola awaka mu Uganda, gamba ng‚Äôokutambula ku sipiidi eyeeyagaza n‚Äôokukola dduyiro wa Kegel okunyweza ebinywa by‚Äôomu kifuba. (ebigambo 33)",
            "Okukakasa nti ofuna endya entuufu okusobola okudda engulu ng‚Äôolina emmere entono mu Uganda, osobola okugezaako okunoonya emmere ey‚Äôebbeeyi era erimu ebiriisa okuva mu butale bw‚Äôomu kitundu. Okugatta ku ekyo, okukozesa olusuku olutono okulima enva endiirwa kiyinza okukuwa ensibuko ennungi ey‚Äôebiriisa ebitonotono ebikulu. (ebigambo 42)",
            "Obubonero obulaga nti weetaaga okugenda mu ddwaaliro mu bwangu ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala wano mu Uganda mulimu okulumwa omutwe ogw‚Äôamaanyi, okulumwa omutima, okulumwa mu kifuba, okunyirira mu lubuto, oba okuvaamu amazzi agawunya obubi mu bukyala, kuba bino biyinza okulaga obuzibu. (ebigambo 34)",
            "Bw‚Äôoba tosobola kugenda mu kifo eky‚Äôebyobulamu olw‚Äôobutabeera bulungi oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mu Uganda, osobola okugezaako okubukakanya ng‚Äôokakasa nti ofuna ekiwummulo ekimala era ng‚Äôonoonya obuyambi n‚Äôobuwagizi okuva mu mikwano n‚Äôabooluganda abakwetoolodde. (ebigambo 34)",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola z‚Äôekinnansi mu Uganda eziyinza okuyamba mu kudda engulu oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala, gamba ng‚Äôokukozesa eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi n‚Äôokusiiga n'amaanyi okukendeeza ku puresha nga tukozesa ebintu eby'obuwangwa, ebitera okuyisibwa mu milembe. (ebigambo 34)",
            "Bw‚Äôofuna ebizibu era nga tolina busobozi kugenda mu ddwaaliro mu Uganda, olina okutegeeza bammemba ba ttiimu y‚Äôebyobulamu ku kyalo mu kitundu oba okukubira mikwano gyo oba ab‚Äôenganda oyambibwe. Mu mbeera enzibu, osobola okugezaako okutuukirira omusawo butereevu okukulwabula. (ebigambo 40)",
            "Enzikiriza oba enkola eza bulijjo mu kitundu kyange wano mu Uganda mulimu okusuubira nti bamaama balina okugulira abaana abatanaba kuzalibwa  obugoye, n‚Äôokukozesa eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi ebitera okuweebwa abazaalisa ab‚Äôekinnansi. (ebigambo 35)",
            "Nedda, nze ku lwange sigoberera nkola ya buwangwa oba enzikiriza yonna entongole wano mu Uganda. Enkola yange etera okwesigamizibwa ennyo ku kumanya okwa bulijjo n‚Äôebyo omuntu by‚Äôayagala okusinga okunywerera ku nnono z‚Äôobuwangwa ezitali zimu. (ebigambo 33)",
            "Mpulira bulungi okubeera maama wano mu Uganda. Okweraliikirira kwe nnalina emabegako kwali kwekuusa ku bbugumu ery‚Äôamaanyi mu mubiri omwana wange lye yafunanga oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokugema, naye ekirungi, ebyo bikendedde. (ebigambo 34)",
            "Nedda, sirina kyembuuza wadde okweraliikirira ku bulamu bwange mu kiseera kino wano mu Uganda.",
            "Okusanyuka wano mu Uganda, nnyumirwa nnyo okulaba firimu, okwogera ne mikwano gyange, n‚Äôokugenda mu kkanisa. Ebikolwa bino binnyamba okuwummulamu n‚Äôokuwulira nga nnina akakwate n'abantu.",
            "Nzikakanya situleesi wano mu Uganda nga njogera n‚Äôomuntu gwe nneesiga, nga mikwano gyange egy‚Äôoku lusegere. Okubabuulira enneewulira zange kinnyamba okugumira ebizibu byonna.",
            "Yee, nkozesa eddagala oba enkola z‚Äôekinnansi, gamba ng‚Äôokukozesa okunyigiriza kw‚Äôeddagala ly'ekinnansia ku nnabaana, nga kino kirowoozebwa nti kiyamba mu kudda engulu oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala.",
            "Yee, nsobodde okukwatagana ne bbebi wange wano mu Uganda, era mpulira bulungi mu nneewulira. Akakwate kano kandeetera essanyu lingi.",
            "Nedda, sirina kibuuzo kyonna oba kye nneeraliikirira ku bulamu bwange mu kiseera kino . Mpulira bulungi.",
            "Mpulira nga waliwo enkyukakyuka mu langi y‚Äôolususu. Nfuba okunaaba buli lunaku",
            "Bw‚Äôoba tosobola kufuna ddagala eriweweeza ku bulumi oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala, okukozesa ekintu ekinyogoga ku bitundu ebikoseddwa kiyinza okuyamba okuweweza obumu ku bulumi.Kisiige mpola okumala akaseera katono emirundi egiwerako olunaku.",
            "Bw‚Äôoba olina obuzibu mu kuwona ekiwundu ky'okulongoosebwa era nga tewali bikozesebwa mu kitundu kyo, kikulu okudda mu kifo ky‚Äôebyobulamu (mu ddwaliro) gye bakulongoseza kwongera okwekebejjebwa n‚Äôokujjanjabibwa.",
            "Bw‚Äôoba toli kumpi na ddwaaliro era nga weetaaga okulabirira ewuzi/ ekiwundu ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala, olina okukakasa nti ekifo ekyo okiyonja bulungi n‚Äôamazzi agatabuddwamu omunnyo omutono, okutangira obuwuka.",
            "Obubonero obulaga nti omuntu alina obulwadde oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mulimu omusujja omungi n‚Äôokufulumya amazzi ng‚Äôawunya. Okwetangira kizingiramu okumira eddagala nga bwe likulagiddwa, okukuuma obuyonjo, n‚Äôokukakasa nti ofuna ekiwummulo ekimala ng‚Äôosaba ab‚Äôomu maka okuyambako mu kukulabirira.",
            "Bw‚Äôoba tosobola kuwummula kimala mu kiseera ky‚Äôokuwona omubiri olw‚Äôobuvunaanyizibwa bw‚Äôamaka, kirungi okweyanjula mu ddwaaliro oba ow'omusawo oweebwe obuwabuzi ku ngeri y‚Äôobukuumi.  ",
            "Bw‚Äôofulumya nnyo omusaayi ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala, olina okugenda amangu ew‚Äôomusawo. Wadde ng‚Äôokudda engulu mu mubiri ne mu nneewulira kikulu, okufulumya omusaayi okutawumula kwetaaga okwekenneenyezibwa omukugu mu by‚Äôobulamu.",
            "Kiyinza okuba ekizibu okulondoola obulungi enkulaakulana yo ey‚Äôokuwona ng'oli waka nga tokebereddwa musawo buli kiseera. Bw‚Äôoba olina ebikweraliikiriza, kirungi nnyo okunoonya obuwabuzi okuva eri omusawo w‚Äôebyobulamu bwe kiba kisoboka.",
            "Yee, eddagala oba enkola z‚Äôomu kitundu eziyinza okuwagira okuwona oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mulimu okussa essira ku ndya yo ng‚Äôolya enva endiirwa nyingi, za mugaso nnyo mu kuwa ebiriisa ebyetaagisa okusobola okuwona.",
            "Bw‚Äôoba olina obuzibu mu kuyonsa ate nga tolina buyambi bwa kuyonsa, amagezi agaweereddwa wano galabika nga gakwatagana n‚Äôokukendeeza obuzito. Ku nsonga z‚Äôokuyonsa, noonya obuyambi okuva eri omukozi w‚Äôebyobulamu kirungi.",
            "Amagezi agaweereddwa wano, okunaaba mu ngalo n‚Äôokuyonja nga bwekisoboka, gakwata ku buyonjo okusinga okuddukanya enkyukakyuka mu buzito oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala. Okugejja oba okweyongera, webuuze ku musawo bwe kiba kisoboka kirungi.",
            "Ekiteeso ky‚Äôokukola dduyiro okwerabira tekikwata butereevu ku kukuuma buyonjo bw‚Äôomuntu. Enkola ezisinga obulungi mulimu okunaaba buli kiseera, okukyusa paadi enfunda eziwera, n‚Äôokwambala engoye ennyonjo okutangira obuwuka.",
            "Bwoba owulira nga ozitoowereddwa era nga tosobola kutuuka ku mubuulirizi ku nsonga z'obulamu bw'obwongo, okwogera n'omusawo mu ddwaaliro ly'omu kitundu kyo kiyinza okukuwa obuwagizi oba obulagirizi ku bikozesebwa ebiriwo.",
            "Okukozesa ekinyogogga okunyinga awazimbye si bujjanjabi obumanyiddwa obw‚Äôokwennyamira okw‚Äôamaanyi oba okweraliikirira oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala. Bwoba ofuna embeera zino, kikulu okunoonya obuyambi okuva eri omukugu mu by‚Äôobulamu mu bwangu.",
            "Ekiddibwamu nti Yee ennyangu tennyonnyola ngeri ya kukendeeza entuuyo n'okuziyira ekiro. Enzikakanya y'ezo mbeera eyinza okubaamu okwambala engoye eziyittamu empewo, okunnywa amazzi noosigala ng'ogalina mu mubiri, n‚Äôokutereeza ebbugumu ly‚Äôekisenge. Bwe kiba nga kya maanyi, weebuuze ku musawo w‚Äôebyobulamu.",
            "Okulya obulungi omuli ebibala n‚Äôenva endiirwa n‚Äôokusigala ng‚Äôolina amazzi mu mubiri kikulu mu kudda engulu oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala, naye dduyiro ow‚Äôenjawulo ng‚Äôokutambula ne Kegels nabyo batera okubisemba okuyamba omubiri okudda engulu.",
            "Okiyamba ku kuvaamu omusaayi omungi tekuddamu ngeri ya kukakasa nti omuntu alina endya entuufu ng'olina emmere entono. Okukulembeza emmere erimu ebiriisa eriwo n'okunoonya amagezi okuva mu bakozi b'ebyobulamu oba ebintu ng'emmere, eddala by'omukitundu kiyinza okuyamba.",
            "Nedda", "yokka si ntuufu. Waliwo obubonero obwetaagisa okugenda mu ddwaaliro mu bwangu, gamba ng‚Äôokuvaamu omusaayi omungi, omusujja ogw‚Äôamaanyi, okulumwa ennyo oba okukaluubirirwa okussa.",
            "Bwoba tosobola kugenda mu ddwaliro olw‚Äôobutabeera bulungi oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala, okunoonya obuyambi okuva eri mmemba wa ttiimu y‚Äôebyobulamu mu kyalo (VHT) mu kitundu kyo kiyinza okukuwa obulagirizi n‚Äôobuyambi.",
            "Okuddamu kwogera ku nzikiriza z'okugema ne enzikiriza z'endya, ezikwatagana n'ebyobulamu naye nga si nkola za nnono ez'okuwona oluvannyuma lw'okuzaala kwennyini. Enkola z‚Äôennono ziyinza okuli eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi oba enkola ez‚Äôenjawulo.",
            "Eky'okuddamu Yee - ekyo kye nzikiriza z'okugema tekikwata butereevu ku kiki ky'olina okukola singa ofuna ebizibu era nga tosobola kutambula. Mu mbeera ng‚Äôezo, okunoonya obuyambi okuva mu bakozi b‚Äôebyobulamu mu kitundu kitera okuba eddaala erisooka.",
            "Okuwulira essanyu olw'obeera maama n'okwagala abaana b'omuntu biba birowoozo bya muntu ku bubwe, si nzikiriza oba enkola eza bulijjo mu kitundu ezikwata ku bulamu oba okuwona.",
            "Okuddamu kulaga nti okutuuka ku ddwaaliro kiyinza okuba ekizibu, nga kuno kusoomoozebwa kwekuusa ku kufuna obujjanjabi, si kituufu nti nkola ya buwangwa oba enzikiriza egobererwa.",
            "Okuddamu kwogera ku kukyalira mikwano n'okufuna obudde okuwummulamu, ekikwatagana n'obulamu obulungi naye nga tekiddamu butereevu nneewulira ku buzadde oba okweraliikirira kwonna.",
            "Okuddamu kunnyonnyola okukakanya situleesi nga ogabana emboozi, ng'eno nkola ya kugumira mbeera, so si kibuuzo oba kweraliikirira ku bulamu bwennyini.",
            "Eiddibwamu nti Nedda ennyangu kiraga nti omuntu oyo talina budde kuwummula oba okwenyigira mu bintu eby'okusanyusa, ekiky'omugaso ennyo ku bulamu bwe obulungi mu kiseera ky'okuwona.",
            "Okuddamu nti Yee kiwulikaka bulungi bulijjo era kilaga essanyu ate n'embeera ennuungi mu birowoozo naye tekinnyonnyola bukodyo bwa kuziyiza situleesi obw'enjawulo noku nti wabaawo omuntu gw'oyogera naye oba nedda, tekyegondwako.",
            "Okuddamu kilungi nnyo kirabika kitegeeza okuwulira obulungi. Okwogera ku dduyiro w‚Äôomubiri, okulya obulungi, n‚Äôokukeberebwa abasawo kinnyonnyola enkola y‚Äôokwefaako naye tekikwata butereevu ku nkwatagana.",
            "[Tewali kuddamu kuweereddwa mu likoda eyasooka.]",
            "[Tewali kuddamu kuweereddwa mu likoda eyasooka.]",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola z‚Äôokuzaala ez‚Äôekinnansi ezirina okwewalibwa okulaba ng‚Äôozaala bulungi. Kikulu okuteesa ku bino n'omusawo  okutegeera enkola eziyinza okuba ez'obulabe.",
            "Okutebenkeza enkola z‚Äôennono n‚Äôamagezi g‚Äôabasawo ag‚Äôomulembe ng‚Äôoli lubuto kizingiramu okulondoola ennyo obulamu bwa maama abakugu mu by‚Äôobulamu n‚Äôokusomesa amaka mu by‚Äôobulamu mu bujjuvu.",
            " Ekidibwamu ekyangu yee kiraga nti waliwo enzikiriza z'obuwangwa eza bulijjo ezikwata ku mbuto n'okuzaala mu kitundu, naye tekirambika nzikiriza ezo kye ziri.",
            "okusomesa bamaama ku by'obulamu ebiva mu nkola z‚Äôokuzaala ez‚Äôennono",
            "Okufiirwa omumwa gwa nnabaana nga maama Engeri y‚Äôokwanguya enkola y‚Äôokuzaala ng‚Äôokozesa eddagala ly'ekinnansi",
            "Okunyikira okumanyisa ennyo bamaama ne bataata",
            "Yee, waliwo pulogulaamu za gavumenti n‚Äôebibiina by‚Äôobwannakyewa (NGOs) mu Uganda ebiwa obuyambi eri abakyala ab‚Äôembuto. Osobola okubuuza mu ddwaaliro mu kitundu kyo oba mu bifo k'ebyobulaamu mu mukitundu ku nteekateeka eziriwo.",
            " Nga bayita mu kuteekawo ebiragiro by'okugoberera n‚Äôokukakasa nti buli musawo w‚Äôekinnansi alina layisinsi/ ebbaruwa emukiriza okukola.",
            "Okuwa bamaama eddagala ly'ekinansi okwanguya okuzaala",
            "okulaga amaka gange obulabe obuyinza okuva mu kukozesa enkola z‚Äôennono.",
            "Yee, waliwo eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi erikozesebwa ng‚Äôoli lubuto mu Uganda, naye kikulu okumanya eritaliiko bulabe era neelyo eririna okwewalibwa. Bulijjo kirungi okwebuuza ku musawo w‚Äôebyobulamu okufuna obulagirizi ku nsonga eno.",
            "Yee, mu Uganda, eddagala  ery‚Äôekinnansi likozesebwa abakazi nga bali embuto. Wabula kikulu nnyo okuzuula obukuumi bw'embuto n‚Äôebiyinza okuba eby‚Äôobulabe. Okunoonya amagezi okuva mu bakugu mu by‚Äôobulamu kirungi.",
            "okumanya ku ddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi ng‚Äôoli lubuto weekuli, ng‚Äôelimu telirina bulabe ate eddala liyinza okuba ely‚Äôobulabe. Kirungi okuteesa ku nkozesa y‚Äôeddagala lyonna ery‚Äôekinnansi n‚Äôomusawo w‚Äôebyobulamu.",
            " Nga tuyita mu kubalaga obulabe obuyinza okubaawo oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokukozesa enkola ez‚Äôekinnansi.",
            "Bayambako mu kuzaala n‚Äôokulabirira nga okusinziira ku biragiro by‚Äôabakozi b‚Äôebyobulamu,",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola z‚Äôobuwangwa ezikwata ku kuzaala mu Uganda eziyinza okukosa obulamu bw‚Äôomwana wo. Kikulu okumanya bino n‚Äôokukubaganya ebirowoozo n‚Äôomusawo w‚Äôebyobulamu okulaba ng‚Äôomwana abeera bulungi.",
            "Nga bayita mu kukuwa ssente osobole okugula eddagala eritali ku ddwaliro.",
            " okukozesa endagala enfumbe okunyiga olubuto lw‚Äôomwana oluvanyuma lw'okuzaala",
            "Nga bayita mu kulabirira obulungi abakai abazadde n‚Äôokubayigiriza enkola ezisinga obulungi ze balina okukozesa era mu ngeri yonna basobola bakomawo.",
            "Yee, mu Uganda, abakulembeze b‚Äôomukitundu oba abakadde batera okukola omulimu ogw'amaanyimu kuyamba okuziba ekituli wakati w‚Äôebyobulamu eby‚Äôennono n‚Äôeby‚Äôomulembe nga bakuza okutegeeragana n‚Äôempuliziganya.",
            "Ndowooza nti yee era kiri nti bawa obulagirizi,okukakasa n'okutumbula enkolagana mu kitundu.",
            "Goberera amateeka n'ebiragiro, by'Empeereza y'okulabirira abakyala ab'embuto.",
            "Enkola ez‚Äôobulabe zisobola okwongera ku bulabe bw‚Äôokukwatibwa yinfekisoni, Enkola ezikwata ku kuzaala n‚Äôokwelabirira wamu n'omwana oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala",
            "Weebuuze ku omukugu we ebyulamu okukubaganya ebirowoozo ku nkola yonna ey‚Äôekinnansi gy‚Äôolowoozaako, bakkirize okwekenneenya obulabe obuyinza okuvaamu",
            "Obutatendekebwa mu by‚Äôobujjanjabi n‚Äôebikozesebwa okukola ku bizibu ebiva mu kuzaala omwana, obuyinza okukwatibwa yinfekisoni olw‚Äôenkola ezitali za buyonjo, obutasobola kuzuula n‚Äôokukakanya embeera ez‚Äôamangu ez‚Äôakabi ennyo n‚Äôokulwawo okunoonya obujjanjabi.",
            "Okusomesa abantu b'omukitundu kijja kuyamba okutereeza enfumo ezikwatagana n'endya.",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola z‚Äôoluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mu Uganda z‚Äôosaanidde okwegendereza. Kirungi bino okubiteesaako n‚Äôomusawo okukakasa nti tebirina bulabe eri okuwona ko n‚Äôobulamu obulungi bw‚Äôomwana.",
            "Osobola okuyingiza abasawo b‚Äôekinnansi mu kwelabirira mu Uganda ate ng‚Äôokakasa nti ofuna obujjanjabi ng‚Äôonoonya enkola y‚Äôenzikiriza etuukana n‚Äôenkola z‚Äôekinnansi n‚Äôokubuulirira kw‚Äôabasawo okw‚Äôomulembe, okukakasa nti ofuna obuyambi bw‚Äôobuwangwa n‚Äôobujjanjabi obwetaagisa.",
            "Enkola z‚Äôemmere ey‚Äôekinnansi ng‚Äôoli lubuto mu Uganda omuli swiiti n‚Äôamasavu oluusi zitwalibwa ng‚Äôez‚Äôomugaso olw'amaanyi, naye okuzirya ekisusse kiyinza okuba eky‚Äôobulabe. Kikulu okutebenkeza enkola z‚Äôemmere ey‚Äôekinnansi n‚Äôokubuulirira ku by‚Äôendya okuva mu bakola ku by‚Äôobulamu.",
            "Beera n'endoowoza nga ngazzi era ow‚Äôekitiibwa ng‚Äôonnyonnyola ensonga lwaki osalawo ng‚Äôoggumiza emigaso gy‚Äôobujjanjabi egy‚Äôokuzaala mu ddwaaliro ate ng‚Äôokkiriza empisa zo ez‚Äôobuwangwa",
            "Eddagala erimu ery‚Äôekinnansi litwalibwa ng‚Äôeritali lya bulabe okukozesa ng‚Äôoli lubuto",
            "Kozesa emikolo/ empisa z‚Äôamazzi amakyafu n‚Äôobukodyo bw‚Äôokuziyiza obulumi ng‚Äôozaala",
            " Okulya emmere entongole erimu ebiriisa",
            "Okuwa amagezi agazuula amangu n'okukendeeza ebizibu ebiyinza okuva mu lubuto",
            "Okuwa abakyala ab‚Äôembuto obuyambi n‚Äôokusomeseza mu kitundu",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola z‚Äôobuwangwa ezikwata ku kuzaala eziyinza okukosa obulamu bw‚Äôomwana wo wano mu Uganda. Kikulu okukubaganya ebirowoozo ku nkola zonna ez‚Äôobuwangwa z‚Äôoteekateeka okugoberera n‚Äôomusawo okukakasa nti tezirina bulabe eri omwana wo.",
            "Bw‚Äôoba osazeewo okugoberera amagezi g‚Äôabasawo ag‚Äôomulembe wano mu Uganda, osobola okunoonya obuwagizi okuva mu kitundu kyo ng‚Äôobakubiriza nabo okukozesa eby‚Äôobulamu era ng‚Äôogabana amawulire agakwata ku migaso gy‚Äôebyobulamu eby‚Äôomulembe eri obulamu bwa bamaama n‚Äôabaana.",
            "Enzikiriza z‚Äôennono ezikwata ku kudda engulu oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mu Uganda mulimu enkola ng‚Äôokukola dduyiro n‚Äôokutuula mu ddagala ly'ekinnansi. Bino bisobola ng'oggaasseko n‚Äôebiteeso by‚Äôabasawo nga bakakasa nti dduyiro asaanira okuwona oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala n‚Äôokukubaganya ebirowoozo ku bulamu bw‚Äôenkola z‚Äôebimera n‚Äôomusawo w‚Äôebyobulamu.",
            "Osobola okukakanya ebisuubirwa mu buwangwa ebikwata ku nkola z‚Äôoluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala ate ng‚Äôokakasa obulamu bwo mu Uganda ng‚Äôoyita mu kusomesa abantu ku by‚Äôobulamu ku nkola z‚Äôobuwangwa ezikwatagana n‚Äôokulabirira maama oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala, okutumbula enkola ezikwatagana n‚Äôobuwangwa n‚Äôokutumbula ebyobulamu.",
            "Yee, mu Uganda, waliwo abakulembeze b‚Äôomukitundu oba abakadde abasobola okuyamba okuziba ekituli wakati w‚Äôokulabirira okw‚Äôekinnansi n‚Äôokw‚Äôomulembe nga bayamba empuliziganya n‚Äôokutegeeragana wakati w‚Äôenkola z‚Äôekinnansi n‚Äôenkola z‚Äôobujjanjabi ez‚Äôomulembe mu kitundu.",
            "Okunywa n'okulya eddagala ly'ekinnansi ku lubuto (okugeza emirandira ja gonja, ejobwo, emugorora)",
            "Kubiriza abakyala b'embuto okugenda mu bujjanjabi oba okwekebejja embuto, okulya emmere ennungi ngelimu ebiriisa byonna, okumira empeke z'ebirungo okugeza fefo, folic, okukuuma obuyonjo, okunoonya omusawo mu budde",
            "1. Okutuula mu ddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi, osobola okuzaala nga tolina bulabe 2. Bw‚Äôolya ettaka oba ebbumba ojja kuzaala omwana omulamu",
            "Okusomesa ebyobulamu n‚Äôokugenda buli kiseera mu ddwaaliro okubebejja olubuto, obutazaalira awaka.",
            "okuvaamu omusaayi wakati mukuzaala/oluvanyuma lw'okuzaala, okuyulika kwa nnabaana, ebissa ebijja amangu nnyo, okufa kwa maama (nakawere), omwana okuzaalibwa nga mufu, omwana nga mulema olw'okuyambibwa mu kuzaala nga bakozessa ebintu eby'enjawulo.",
            "Okusomesa ebyobulamu, okukubiriza abakyala b'embuto okugenda kukebejjebwa, endya ennungi, okuzalira mu ddwaliro, weewale eddagala ly'ekinnansi",
            "Okwegatta nga bukyali nga wiiki 6 tezinnaba kutuuka, Okufuuwa oba okuteeka obusa bw‚Äôente ku kalira, weewale emirimu eminene, weewale eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi",
            " Okutendeka abazaalisa ab'ekinnansi ku kuzaala mu ngeri etali ya bulabe n'engeri y'okuzuula ebizibu ebiva ku lubuto, okutendekebwa ku ngeri y'okukozesaamu IPPs (Enkola z'okuziyiza obulwadde) n'okusindikibwa bwe kiba kyetaagisa",
            "Enkola y‚Äôokurya emmere ennungi: 1. Kubiriza nakawere okunywa obusera bw'obulo n‚Äôokulya karo okwongera ekiriisa kya iron (ekyuma) omu mubiri, enva endiirwa. 2. okukuuma bamaama nga baddibwamu amazzi. Enkola ez‚Äôobulabe: 1. Okwewala okulya ennyama n‚Äôamagi ekivaako obutaba na puloteyina 2. Okulya emmere enkalu atte nga ngumu ng‚Äôayolekera okuzaala kibawa okuziyira 3. Okubeera enjala nga boolekedde obudde bw‚Äôokuzaala kibaleetera okulemererwa okusika abaana 4. Abamu babuuka ebiseera byokuulya ate mu kifo ky‚Äôekyo baweebwa eddagala ly'ekinnansi ekifuula omwana ne maama okubeera n‚Äôendya embi.",
            "Okubuulirira amaka ku migaso gy'okuzaalira mu ddwaaliro n'obukuumi bw'obulamu eri omwana ne maama",
            "Nedda, eddagala lyonna ely'ekinnansi lirina okwewalibwa olw‚Äôemiwendo (egyokunywa) egitamanyiddwa",
            "Sigala ng‚Äôokubiriza bamaama okugenda mu bifo oba amalwaliro ag‚Äôomulembe basobole okufuna ebisingawo ku ngeri ennungi bwe bazaalira mu ddwaaliro",
            "1. Okunywa omwenge kuleeta amabeere 2. Nga tutuula mu ddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi 3. Okunywa eddagala ly'ekinnansi Biyinza okukozesebwa ku15-03-2025 Okunywa n‚Äôokulya obulo ne muwogo n‚Äôennyama, ebijanjaaloo nn'ebinyeebwa.",
            "Nga bayita mu masinzizo, mu mikolo gy'okuziika, mu mabaga,;.. Emigaso gy‚Äôokulabirira abakyala b'embuto (nga tebannazaala) okukyusa endowooza n‚Äôenzikiriza zaabwe",
            "Babawa fefo, nga bakola ku mbeera ez‚Äôamangu eza maama mu mutendera ogw‚Äôokubiri ogw‚Äôokuzaala",
            "Eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi eriyinza okuvaako okuzaala amangu, okunyigirizibwa kw‚Äôomwana ali mu lubuto, okukwatibwa nnabaana n‚Äôokufa kw‚Äôomwana ali mu lubuto",
            "Yita mu ssentebe wokukyalo LC 1 okuyita olukiiko lw'abantu b'omukitundu, kwatagana ne VHT",
            "Endya ennungi, okunywa obusera bw'obulo, okukuuma, obuyonjo, okuyonsa n‚Äôokwenyiga n'amazzi agabuguma ng‚Äôomaze okuzaala",
            "Okunaaba mu mazzi agabuguma n‚Äôebikoola by'endagala, okuyonsa, okulya emmere ennungi (ennyama, ebyennyanja, amata n‚Äôbulo) .",
            "Yee, mu Uganda, abakulembeze b‚Äôolukiiko lw‚Äôebitundu (LCs), Ttiimu z‚Äôebyobulamu mu byalo (VHTs), n‚Äôabakulembeze b‚Äôekkanisa/klezia batera okuyamba okuziba ekituli wakati kw‚Äôebyobulamu eby‚Äôennono n‚Äôeby‚Äôomulembe nga bawa obulagirizi n‚Äôokutumbula okutegeeragana mu kitundu.",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola ez‚Äôekinnansi ezikozesebwa mu kuzaala ezirina okwewalibwa okulaba okutumbula okuzaala obulungi mu Uganda. Kikulu okuteesa ku bino n'omusawo w'ebyobulamu okutegeera enkola ki eziyinza okuba ez'obulabe.",
            "Osobola okutebenkeza enkola z‚Äôekinnansi n‚Äôobuwabuzi bw‚Äôabasawo obw‚Äôomulembe ng‚Äôoli lubuto mu Uganda ng‚Äôogoberera amateeka n‚Äôebiragiro ebiweebwa abakugu mu by‚Äôobulamu era ng‚Äôogenda mu mpeereza z‚Äôabasawo mu kiseera ng'oli lubuto buli kiseera.",
            "Enzikiriza z‚Äôobuwangwa eza bulijjo ku nsonga z‚Äôembuto n‚Äôokuzaala mu Uganda mulimu okusala akalira okwewala omuguwa gwaako n‚Äôokumira eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi nga balowooza nti liyamba okuzaala abaana abayonjo ennyo.",
            "Okukakasa nti enkola z‚Äôekinnansi ez‚Äôokuzaala tezitaataaganya bulamu bwo oba obw‚Äôomwana wo mu Uganda, kikulu okwebuuza ku bakugu mu by‚Äôobulamu ku nkola yonna ey‚Äôekinnansi gy‚Äôoteekateeka okugoberera.",
            "Obulabe obuli mu kukozesa abazaalisa ab‚Äôekinnansi mu Uganda buyinza okubamu obulabe bw‚Äôokukwatibwa ebidwadde. Obulabe buno busobola okukendeezebwa nga bulijjo ogenda mu bakugu mu by‚Äôobulamu okebeza embuto n‚Äôokuzaala bwe kiba kisoboka.",
            "Osobola okukola ku ndowooza enkyamu ez‚Äôobuwangwa ku kubulabirizi bw'olubuto  n‚Äôab‚Äôomu maka go mu Uganda ng‚Äôoyita mu kusomesa abantu b‚Äôomukitundu eby‚Äôobulamu, ng‚Äôogabana amawulire amatuufu agakwata ku migaso gy‚Äôobulabirizi bw'olubuto.",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola z‚Äôoluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mu Uganda z‚Äôosaanidde okwegendereza. Kirungi okuteesa n‚Äôomusawo ku bino okukakasa nti tebirina bulabe eri okuwona kwo obulungi bw‚Äôomwana.",
            "Okukolagana n‚Äôabasawo b‚Äôekinnansi n‚Äôebyobulamu nga babasomesa ku magezi g‚Äôabasawo ag‚Äôomulembe ku nsonga z‚Äôembuto n‚Äôokuzaala.",
            "1. Okulya emmere enkalu okumalawo okuziyira 2. Okulya ettaka ekkalu (Emmumba) okukendeeza omuze gw'okulya ebintu ebitasaana kulibwa ng'etakka, choka nebilara.",
            "Okussa essira ku migaso gy‚Äôokukyalira eddwaaliro n‚Äôokukkiriza emigaso n‚Äôempisa z‚Äôobuwangwa",
            "Yee, waliwo eddagala ly‚Äôekinnansi erikozesebwa ng‚Äôoli lubuto mu Uganda, naye kikulu nnyo okumanya eritaliiko bulabe era eririna okwewalibwa. Kirungi okwebuuza ku musawo ku ddagala eryenjawulo.",
            "Okuzuula enzikiriziganya wakati w‚Äôenkola z‚Äôennono n‚Äôez‚Äôomulembe mu kuzaala mu Uganda kiyinza okuzingiramu okuyingizaamu emikolo oba empisa ez‚Äôenjawulo ez‚Äôobuwangwa ate nga n‚Äôobukodyo obw‚Äôomulembe obw‚Äôokuziyiza obulumi mu kiseera ky‚Äôokuzaala mu ddwaliro.",
            "Enkola z‚Äôobuwangwa eza bulijjo ezikwata ku kubulabirizi oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mu Uganda zitera okuzingiramu okulya emmere entongole eteeberezebwa okuyamba okuwona. Bino bisobola okukyusibwamu awatali bulabe nga okakasa nti birimu ebiriisa era nga bituukana n‚Äôebiragiro by‚Äôabasawo okuwona.",
            "Osobola okusomesa ekitundu kyo mu Uganda ku migaso gy‚Äôokwekebekejja olubuto, okusinziira ku nkola z‚Äôekinnansi ng‚Äôowa amawulire amategeerekeka ku bukulu bw‚Äôokuzuula amangu n‚Äôokukakanya ebizibu ebiva byo olubuto eri obulamu bwa maama n‚Äôomwana.",
            "Mu bifo eby‚Äôomulembe eby‚Äôobujjanjabi bw‚Äôabazadde mu Uganda, abazaalisa ab‚Äôannansi basobola okukola kinene mu kuwa obuyambi obusinziira mu kitundu, emirundi mingi nga bawa obuyambi mu nneewulira n‚Äôobuwangwa eri abakyala ab‚Äôembuto n‚Äôamaka gaabwe, oluusi nga bakolera wamu n‚Äôabakugu mu by‚Äôobulamu.",
            "Yee, waliwo enkola z‚Äôobuwangwa ezikwata ku kuzaala mu Uganda eziyinza okukosa obulamu bw‚Äôomwana wo. Kikulu okumanya bino n‚Äôokukubaganya ebirowoozo n‚Äôomusawo okulaba ng‚Äôomwana abeera bulungi.",
            "Bwoba osazeewo okugoberera amagezi g‚Äôabasawo ag‚Äôomulembe mu Uganda, osobola okunoonya obuwagizi okuva mu kitundu kyo ng‚Äôobakubiriza nabo okukozesa empeereza y‚Äôamalwaliro n‚Äôokugabana amawulire agakwata ku migaso gy‚Äôebyobulamu eby‚Äôomulembe eri obulamu bwa bamaama n‚Äôabaana.",
            "Enzikiriza z‚Äôennono ezikwata ku kudda engulu oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala mu Uganda zitera okubeeramu enkola ng‚Äôokukola dduyiro w‚Äôomubiri. Bino bisobola okugattibwa n‚Äôokuteesa kw‚Äôabasawo nga bakakasa nti dduyiro ono temuli bulabe era nga wa mugaso eri okuwona oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala, nga bwe bawabulwa abakugu mu by‚Äôobulamu.",
            "Osobola okuddukanya ebisuubirwa mu buwangwa ebikwata ku nkola z‚Äôoluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala ate ng‚Äôokakasa obulamu bwo mu Uganda ng‚Äôoyita mu kusomesa abantu ku by‚Äôobulamu ku nkola ezitali za bulabe era ez‚Äôomugaso oluvannyuma lw‚Äôokuzaala nga weesigama ku kuteesa kw‚Äôabasawo, okutumbula okusalawo okutuufu.",
            "Yee, mu Uganda, emirundi mingi wabaawo abakulembeze b‚Äôomukitundu oba abakadde abasobola okukola omulimu omukulu mu kuyamba okuziba ekituli wakati w‚Äôebyobulamu eby‚Äôennono n‚Äôeby‚Äôomulembe nga batumbula okutegeeragana n‚Äôokukolagana wakati w‚Äôenkola zombi.",
            "Ne bwe kiba nti eddwaaliro ly‚Äôomu kitundu liri wala nnyo n‚Äôawaka wo mu Uganda, kirungi okugendayo okukebejjibwa nga tonnazaala waakiri emirundi ena ng‚Äôoli lubuto, wadde ng‚Äôegisinga obulungi, omuwendo gw‚Äôokugendayo giba munaana okwekebejja okujjuvu.",
            "Mu byalo mu Uganda, eby‚Äôokulondako eby‚Äôokujjanjaba bamaama ku bwereere oba ku ssente entono bitera okuli okukyalira Ttiimu z‚Äôebyobulamu mu byalo (VHTs), ezisobola okukuwa obujjanjabi obumu obusookerwako n‚Äôokukuyunga ku bifo by‚Äôebyobulamu ebituufu.",
            "Bwoba tosobola kwesasulira kukeberebwa n‚Äôeddagala eriragiddwa ng‚Äôoli lubuto mu Uganda, olina okugenda mu ddwaaliro lya gavumenti erikuli okumpi, kubanga batera okuwa obujjanjabi obw‚Äôebbeeyi ensamusamu.",
            "Kubila ambulance ey‚Äôamangu bw‚Äôoba olina enamba, sigala ng‚Äôokwatagana n'omuzalisa",
            "Yee, mu Uganda, waliwo abakozi b‚Äôebyobulamu abebeera mu kitundu, abatera okusangibwa nga bakola mu malwaliro g‚Äôabaana abazaalibwa nga tebannazaala, abasobola okukeberebwa nga tebannazaala n‚Äôokuwa amagezi ku bulamu bwa bamaama n‚Äôabaana mu kitundu.",
            "Tuukirira aba ambyulensi ez‚Äôamangu. , Bulijjo teekayo ku ssente z'entambula",
            "Obutamanya , Obutabeera na bakozi be by'obulamu abatendeke , obutaba na mpeke ez'omulembe",
            "Bulijjo kolagana n'emikwano, n'ab'awaka wamu n'abakozi b‚Äüebyobulamu",
            "Yee, mu Uganda, waliwo enteekateeka za gavumenti n‚Äôebibiina by‚Äôobwannakyewa ebiwa obuyambi eri abakyala ab‚Äôembuto. Mu bino mulimu enteekateeka ezigendereddwamu okutumbula empeereza y‚Äôebyobulamu mu banakkawere n‚Äôabaana, okuwa abantu okufuna obujjanjabi, n‚Äôokuwa eby‚Äôenjigiriza n‚Äôebikozesebwa. Osobola okubuuza mu bifo by‚Äôebyobulamu mu kitundu oba mu bifo by‚Äôabantu okumanya ebisingawo ku nteekateeka ezenjawulo eziri mu kitundu kyo. Ebimu ku bibiina ebimanyiddwa kuliko Marie Stopes Uganda, UNFPA Uganda, n‚Äôebirala ebikola ku by‚Äôobulamu bwa bamaama n‚Äôabaana.",
            "Funa omuzaalisa akukolera enteekateeka ekunyumira era bulijjo jjukira obulamu businga okukola tewali bulamu tewali mulimu",
            "Kozesa VHTs mu kitundu kyo bamanyi amaddwaliro. Era buuza okuva mu bakulembeze b'ebitundu.",
            "Kozesa empeereza za VHT oba enkambi ezitegekeddwa mu bitundu",
            "Sigala ng‚Äôokwatagana n‚Äôomukozi w‚Äôebyobulamu okufuna obuwabuzi.",
            "Genda mu malwaliro ga gavumenti",
            "Ba VHTs weebali naye era buuza n‚Äôabakulembeze b‚Äôebitundu",
