            "Eego, hariho eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira nk'okukoresa emibazi y'ekishaka/ y'obuhangwa.",
            "Ninkyendeeza oburemeezi obwo ndikweshongora.",
            " Eego, hariho emibazi nainga emitwarize y'obuhangwa ei ndikukoresa.",
            "Nigyezaho kutaho enkoragana nungi n'omwana wangye kandi nyine okushemererwa kwingi.",
            "Eego nyine obusaasi bukye omu nda-nto.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa nintaayaayira banywani bangye.",
            "Nimpurira gye hati. Ninyerinda kurabira omu kurya kurungi n'okukora ebisasaizi ebirikubaasisa kunkiza bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            " Enkora eya buriijo omu kicweka kyangye n'okukoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa kuragurira obusaasi.",
            "Eego, hariho eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira. Ebi nibikwata aha migyenzo erikukwata aha kuzaara n'obwire bwanyima y'okuzaara, ebiragiirwe kuruga omu mirembe omu bantu baitu kandi ebirikutwarwa nk'eby'omugasho aha magara g'abakazi n'abaana.",
            "Nimpurira gye munonga ahabw'okuba maama, n'ekintu kirungi munonga, kandi hati, nshemereirwe kugira ngu tinyine nshonga nz'omutaano ezirikukwata aha buzaire. Ninyumirwa obwire obu n'omwana wangye kandi nkata amaani aha magara gaitu.",
            "Ngaaha, obwahati, tinyine bibuuzo nainga okwerarikirira ebirikukwata aha magara gangye. Nimpurira nk'orikukira kurungi kandi nyine amagara marungi, kwonka ninza kugamba n'abashaho, haaba hariho ekihindukire, nainga haabaho okwerarikirira omu biro by'omumaisho.",
            "Ngaaha, nk'oku naagambire kare, hati tinyine bibuuzo by'omutaano ebirikukwata nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye. Nimpurira kurungi, kwonka ninyetegyereza omugasho gw'oburungi bw'amagara gangye omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, nyine obusaasi n'obutabeerwagye bwanyima y'okuzaara ahabw'okuba nkatunga obuhuta, kandi eky'obusaasi, tibutarikujanjaabwa. Eki kihindwire obwire bw'okubanza bwanyima y'okuzaara eky'oburemeezi omu by'omubiri n'okutambura nk'oku ndikukira.",
            "Ninyonsa omwana wangye emirundi mingi nyomushana na nyekiro, buri murundi ogu omwana arikwenda. Okubyara munonga nikureetera omwana okwiguta, nk'oku arikukira kureebeka nk'oshemereirwe bwanyima y'okwonsa, ekirikumpuumuriza n'okugaruramu amaani.",
            "Ngaaha, tinkareebireho mpindahinduka y'amaani omu kurya nainga okubyama kw'omwana wangye. Okurya n'okubyama kwe nkuhamire kuruga obu bazaarwa, ekimpwera kumanya ebyetengo bye n'okutebeekanisa kurugiirira aharibyo.",
            "Ngaaha, n'ekirungi, tihariho bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire nainga omushwija omuriinye nainga omwana wangye. Twembi tutwire twine obutagasi bwa butoosha kandi titurikworeka obumanyiso bw'oburwaire bwona, ekirikutureetera oburuhuuko bwingi.",
            "Ntwire ninkoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa nk'omuringo gw'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, ekirikukorwa munonga hanuya. Omu muringo ogu ndikwehuriramu, nimbaasa kugira ngu ndiyo ninkira mporampora, n'obu haraabe hakiriho oburemeezi obu ndikureeberereza.",
            "Ngaaha, tihaine omuhwezi bwona omuka.  Ninkakora emirimo y'omuka erikwetengwa mpeekire omwana aha mugongo. Nikinkoresa munonga omu mubiri, kwonka nikinyikiriza kuguma ndi haihi n'omwana wangye obwo ndikukora emirimo yangye.",
            "Nimbasa kuhuumura nyekiro bwonka, kandi nabwo, buriijo nikitaataaganisibwa. Eihangwe, ntaine buhwezi omuka n'omwereere w'okureeberera, obwire bw'okuhuumuraho nibukye munonga, nahabwekyo obwire bw'ekiro nibwo bwire bwangye bw'okubyama.",
            "Ningyezaho kurya kurungi obumwe n'obumwe, kandi eby'okurya byangye birimu ebittokye, obuhunga, ebihimba, ebinyoobwa hamwe na mukene. Ebi nibyo by'okurya ebirikukira kuba biriho kandi ebirimu ebiriisa, ebi ndikugyenderera kurya okumpwera kukira n'okwonsa.",
            "Nimbasa kuhuumuraho kakye nyekiro, kandi eki ndikukoresa okushemererwa n'okugaaniirira aha simu yangye. N'omuringo gwangye gw'okuhikaana n'abandi n'okugarukamu amaani ahanyima y'okureeberera omwana n'okukora emirimo y'omuka.",
            "Nikindeetera okushemererwa kuba maama kandi ninkunda omwooga gwangye omutsya. Obwahati, tinyine nshonga nkuru erikukwata aha kuzaara; ninteekateeka aha kukwatanisa n'omwana wangye n'okutwaaza buri eizooba nk'oku ririkwija.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikuhurira nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omu maka nainga abantu b'omukyanga. Okureeberera buri kimwe nyenka kigumire munonga, kandi obumwe n'obumwe nimpurira obutabaasa kureeberera omwana n'emirimo y'omuka.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikubaasa kuhuumura kurungi kuruga obu nazaara. Ahabw'obutagira buhwezi omuka hamwe n'ebyetaago by'omwana w'omwereere, okutunga obwire bw'okuhuumura kurungi kigumire, kandi buriijo ninyehurira nduhire munonga.",
            "Eego,ninyerarikirira munonga. Obujunanizibwa bw'okureeberera omwereere, hamwe n'okuburwa obuhwezi hamwe n'okwereeberera, obumwe nikireeta okwerarikirira n'okutiina.",
            "Eego, hariho eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira. Ebi n'eby'obuhangwa bwaitu kandi nibituhabura oku tushemereire kwereeberera hamwe n'abaana baitu bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Ninkira kukora aha buremeezi obwo ndikugyezaho kubyama kyaba nikibaasika, hamwe n'okushaba, ekirikumpuumuriza n'okumpa amaani. N'obu ndikushanga okuhuumurizibwa omu bikorwa ebi, tinkagambire aha kugira omuntu w'okugamba nawe omu nshonga egi.",
            "Eego,ninkoresa emibazi y'enzaarwa, okukira munonga ey'obuhangwa, erikukira kureebeka omu buhangwa bwaitu, ahabw'ebyetaago by'amagara bitari bimwe na bimwe, otwariiremu n'okutereera bwanyima y'okuzaara hamwe n'okugira amagara marungi.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye kandi ninkyehurirmu gye. N'obu haraabe hariho oburemeezi bw'obuhwezi bukye n'okuhuumuraho kukye, okukwatanisa n'omwana wangye n'okw'amaani kandi n'okw'omugasho munonga.",
            "Eego, nyine okwerarikirira aha magara gangye, okukira munonga enshonga z'okwesiga omukundwa wangye, ekirikutuma naguma ninyetenga okuhurizagana n'omushaija wangye obutoosha kurabira omu kuhandiika obutumwa n'omushaija wangye kugira ngu ampumurize n'okutuubya aha kwerarikirira kwangye.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kugaaniira n'abanywani bangye aha simu yangye, obwire bwona obu nyine obwire, obwir obwingi ninkikora nyekiro. Naaba nyine obwire burikumara obw'okuhuumuraho, tiburikumara ahabw'obujunaanizibwa bwangye bwemirimo y'omuka hamwe n'omwana.",
            "Nyine enteekateeka y'okwereeberera, ntiire  amaani ahari ebyo ebi ndikubaasa kurugiirira aha mbeera yangye eriho hati. Eki nikitwariramu okugyezaho kurya ebyokurya ebirimu ebiriisa n'okurinda obuyonjo bwange nk'omuntu, nobu kyakuba kitorobi kutunga obwire bw'okwereeberera.",
            "Enyikiriza eya buriijo omu kicweka kyangye n'okukoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa omu migasho mingi y'eby'amagara, otwariiremu n'obwire bwa bwanyima y'okuzaara. Emibazi y'obuhangwa egi neetwarwa nk'omuringo gw'obuhangwa gw'okukiza n'okureetaho amagara marungi.",
            "Eego, hariho engyenderwaho z'eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira, nobu ndaabe ntarikukuratira zoona. Ninkira kukoresa ebyo ebi ndikukimanya kandi ebi ndikuteekateeka ngu nibiija kuba eby'omugasho aha kukira kwangye n'okureeberera omwana wangye.",
            "Eego, ninyehurira gye ahabw'okuba maama, nikireeta enyehuriira erikuha amaani, kandi obwahati, tinyine ebirikutiinisa ebikwatiraine n'omurimo gwangye nk'omuzaire omusya. Ninteekateeka munonga aha kushemererwa kw'obuzaire.",
            "Eego, nyine eky'okwerarikirira ekirikukwata aha magara gangye, n'ekyetengo ky'okukyeberwa akakooko ka siriimu buri kaire. Eki n'ekintu ekiri omu biteekateeko byangye, kandi nimpurira ngu n'eky'omugasho kuguma ninfayo ahabw'amagara gangye.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa, ninkunda kugaaniira na banywani bangye aha simu yangye, kandi natunga omugisha, ningyezaho kubyama. Ababw'okuba n'omereere, obwire bw'okushemererwa ni bukye, nahabwekyo obwire bukye obu nibwo nyine obw'okushemererwa.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikugyezaho kubyama, okushaba amaani n'obusingye, n'okugamba n'omushaija wangye, orikumpa obuhwezi n'okunyegyereza omu bwire obu obw'oburemeezi.",
            "Eego,ninkoresa emibazi y'enzaarwa, okukira munonga egyo erikukoresa eby'obuhangwa, ekirikumanywa munonga omu ntwaza yaitu y'eby'amagara n'amagara marungi n'bugwagye, okukira munonga omu bwire bwa bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye kandi nikyehurira gye. Enkoragana egi erikweyongyera n'oburugo bw'okushemererwa n'okunyweza enkoragana yangye n'omwana wangye.",
            "Ngaaha, omu bwire obu, tinyine bibuuzo ebirikukwata aha magara gangye. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'okureeberera omwana wangye, kwonka ninza kuronda obuhabuzi bw'abashaho, kyaba nikyetengwa.",
            "Nimpurira gye aha omubiri gwangye, kandi ninyereeberera kurabira omu kugyezaho kukora ebisasaizi obu ndikubaasa n'okurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa byona, okunyamba okukira n'okwongyera aha amaani gangye.",
            "Eego, nyine obusaasi bw'omunda, ekintu eki ntwiire nimpurira kuruga obu nazaara. N'obusaasi oburikugumaho obu ndikuteekateeka ngu nibwija kukyendeera nk'oku ndikugumizamu n'okutereera bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Ninyonsa omwana wangye ku arikurira, ekirikubaho emirundi mingi omu eizooba ryona. Nikireebeka ngu okwonka oku okurikwetengwa nikuhwera okureeba ngu omwana yaaguma ayigusi, nk'oku buriijo arikureebeka nk'orikumarwa bwanyima y'okwonsa.",
            "Ngaaha, tinkareebireho mpindahinduka y'amaani omu kurya kw'omwana wangye nainga oku arikubyama. Atwire ataine mpinduka kuruga obu azaarwa, ekirikumpwera kwetegyereza ebyetengo bye hamwe n'emitwarize ye.",
            "Ngaaha, ekirungi, tihariho bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire nainga omushwija omuriinye nainga omwana wangye. Twembi tutwire turigye omu magara kandi titurikworeka bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire.",
            "Ntwire ninyoga n'amaizi garikwotsya, kugira ngu mbone kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Omuringo ogu nigureebeka nk'ogurikuhuumuriza omubiri gwangye, okutwarira hamwe. Nimpurira ndikukira mporampora, n'obu ebiro ebimwe birikuba biri birungi kukira ebindi.",
            "Eego, nyine obuhwezi omuka, ekiri ekyomugasho munonga omu kubaasa kukora  emirimo y'obutoosha n'okureeberera omwana. Obuhwezi obu nibumpa obwire bwingi kuteekateeka aha kukira endwara y'omunda ei naagambireho.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura, n'obu obwire bw'okubyama bwangye burikuba butarikushushana kurugiirira aha byetaago by'omwana. Okugira obuhwezi omuka, nikimpwera kutunga obwire bw'okuhuumura eizooba ryona n'ekiro kyona.",
            "Eego, ntwire nindya kurungi, ntiire amaani aha by'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa nka ebitookye, ekirikukoresibwa munonga omu kyanga eki, ebihimba ebirikuyamba omu kwombeka omubiri, hamwe n'ebyenyanja, oburugo burungi by'ebiriisa ebirikuhwera omu kukira kurungi bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura, kandi eki ndikukora okushemererwa n'okuza omu kanisa. Nikindeetera obusingye n'obuhwezi, ekirikubaasa kumpeereza akahuumuro kuruga omu buremeezi bw'okureeberera omwana w'omwereere.",
            "Nimpurira gye munonga ahabw'okuba maama; n'ekintu kirungi munonga, kandi hati, nshemereirwe kugira ngu tinyine nshonga yoona erikukwata aha nshonga yangye nk'omuzaire omusya.",
            "Eego, nimpurira nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omu maka gangye. Okubaho kwabo hamwe n'okwenda kumpwera kwabo, bimbaasize munonga omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara, okuheereza obuhwezi oburikumara n'obw'ebiteekateeko.",
            "Eego, mbaasize kuhuumura kurungi byanyima y'okuzaara, okukira munonga ahabw'okugira ngu nyine abantu abarikumpwera omu mirimo etari emwe n'emwe, ekirikunyikiriza kuhuumura kurungi.",
            " Ngaaha, tindikukira kwerarikirira okukira buriijo. N'obu haraabe hariho empindahinduka ezishemereire kukorwa ahabw'omwana muto, ninyehurira nyine obucureera n'obwegyendesereza.",
            "Eego, hariho engyenderwaho z'eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira, nk'okunaabisa omwana enshabiko, n'enyikiriza ngu omuntu tashemereire kugarukamu omuntu weena orikweta eiziina rye yaaba nayonsa, ahabw'okuba nikibaasa kureetera amashereka kuguruka.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikuza omu kanisa, ahu ndikushanga obusingye n'obuhwezi omu bantu. N'obu ndikutunga okuhuumurizibwa omu kwikiriza kwangye, tinkagambire aha kugira omuntu w'okugamba nawe omu nshonga egi.",
            "Eego,nimpa eifubo kandi ninkira kukoresa emibazi y'enzaarwa. Ebi n'ekicweka ky'omugasho omu buhangwa bwaitu, kandi ninshanga bingi ahari byo biri eby'omugasho aha magara n'obugwagye, namunonga omu bwire bwa bwanyma y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye, kandi nikishemeza munonga. Enkoragana egi n'oburugo bw'okushemererwa n'okunyweza omukago gwaitu burizooba.",
            "Ngaaha, tinyine bibuuzo nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye obwahati. Nimpurira gye kandi ntiire omutima aha kukira kwangye n'okureeberera omwana wangye.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda okuza omu kanisa, ekirikureetaho obumwe n'obusingye. Yaaba nyine obwire bwingi bw'okuhuumura, n'obwire bukye n'omwana omwereere, kwonka obwire obu omu kanisa n'omuringo gw'okuhuumura ahariinye.",
            "Tindikuhurira kubi aha mubiri gwangye obwo ndikukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ninyereeberera ndi kurabira omu kugyezaho kurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa n'okuhuumura ekirikumara, n'obu okushanga obwire bw'okwerinda munonga kurikubaasa kuba okuremeera n'omwereere.",
            "Enyikiriza eya buriijo omu kicweka kyangye n'okukoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa ahabw'emigasho mingi y'eby'amagara, otwariiremu obwire bw'okuzaara n'ahanyima y'okuzaara. Emibazi egi ey'obuhangwa neyikirizibwa kandi neekoresibwa munonga.",
            "Eego, hariho eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira. Ezi nizikwata aha migyenzo y'okuzaara, okureeberera abaana, hamwe n'amagara marungi, n'ezomugasho munonga aha bantu baitu.",
            "Nimpurira gye munonga ahabw'okuba maama; n'ekintu kirungi munonga, kandi obwahati tihaine nshonga yoona aha buzaire. Ninkunda obwire nyumirwa obwire obu obw'omutaano.",
            "Ngaaha, obwire obu, tinyine bibuuzo nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye hamwe n'omwana.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda okuza omu kanisa/klezia, ekirikureetaho obumwe n'obusingye . Obwire bw'okuhuumuraho nibukye, kwonka n'obw'omugasho ahariinye.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikushoma Baiburi n'okuza omu kanisa/klezia, ekirikumpumuriza. Eego, nyine n'abantu b'omuka abu ndikubaasa kugamba nabo okumpwera ku ndikwehurira nyine oburemeezi.",
            "Eego,ninkoresa emibazi y'enzaarwa, okukira munonga ey'obuhangwa, n'omuringo gw'eby'obuhangwa aha amagara n'obugwa gye, okukira munonga bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye, kandi kikandeetera kwehurira gye munonga. Enkoragana egi n'oburugo bw'okushemererwa kw'amaani kandi neeyongyera amaani omukukwatanisa kwaitu.",
            "Ngaaha, tihaine eki ndikwenda kwebuuza aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira hamwe n'amagara marungi g'omwana wangye.",
            "Hati nyehurira gye omu mubiri. Ninyerinda ndikurya kurungi, nkata amaani aha by'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa, kandi nkakora n'eby'okukoresa ebirikubaasa kumpwera kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikuhurira busaasi bwingi bwanyima y'okuzaara. Nyine amagara marungi omu mubiri, ekirikumpwera kuta omutima aha kureeberera omwana wangye.",
            "Ninyonsa omwana wangye emirundi eshatu buri eizooba. Kwonka, buriijo omwana tarikumarwa, obundi n'ahabw'okugira ngu nimuteera amashereka omu cupa ku ndikuza kukora, ekirikuteganisa enkora yaitu y'okwonsa.",
            "Eego, ndeebira ngu omwana wangye naabyama munonga. N'obu abaana b'abereere baraabe nibabyama munonga, ninyegyendesereza kureeba ngu yaarya/ kurungi yaayonka kandi yahika aha bigyendererwa bye by'okukura.",
            " Ngaaha, n'ekirungi, tihariho bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire nainga omushwija omuriinye nainga omwana wangye. Twembi tutwire nitugira obutagasi burungi, kandi titurikworeka bubonero oburikworeka ngu twine oburwaire.",
            "Tinkozire kintu kyona ky'omutaano ahabw'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, kandi nimpurira gye. Okukira kwangye nikureebeka kuriyo nikugyenda omu maisho, eki ninkisiima kandi ninfayo kureeberera omwana wangye.",
            " Eego, nyine obuhwezi omuka, ekiri  eky'omugasho munonga omu kukora emirimo y'omuka n'okureeberera omwana. Obuhwezi obu nibumpwera omu kukukira n'okureeberera ebyetaago by'omwana wangye.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura kumara eshaaha mukaaga kuhisya munaana, n'obu okubyama kwangye kurikuba nikuteganisibwa ahabwokuba omwana naakira kurira nyekiro, ekirikutuma kyangumira munonga okuhuumura omurundi gumwe.",
            "Ntwire nindya, kandi eby'okurya byangye nibitwariramu ebitookye n'ebihimba. N'obu ebi birikuba biri ebyokurya ebirimu ebiriisa, ningyezaho okureeba ngu ntunga ebiriisa ebindi ebirikubaasa kumpwera kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara n'okuyonsa.",
            "Eego, obumwe n'obumwe nimpuumura, kandi eki ndikukoresa okushemererwa n'okureeba tiivi. N'omuringo gwanguhi gw'okuhuumuraho n'okuruhuukwa aha mirimo y'obutoosha y'okureeberera omwaerere",
