            "Eego, ntwire nindya kurungi, ntiire amaani aha by'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa nka ebitookye, ebirikukoresibwa munonga aha hamwe n'ebihimba, omuceeri hamwe n'emboga ezindi nyingi, okumpwera kukira n'okwonsa.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhumura kandi ahabw'okuushemererwa ninkunda kuza omu myanya youkushemerererwamu nobu kwa kuba okutamburaho nainga okutayaayaho kakye. Obwire obu nibumpwera kugaruka busya n'okugira akakwate n'omwanya gw'aheeru.  ",
            "Ninyesiimisa munonga okuba maama, n'enyehurira nungi kandi erikuhikiriza kandi hati nshemereirwe kwatura ngu tinyine nshonga yoona erikukwata aha murimo gwangye nk'omuzaire omusya.",
            "Eego nimpurira ngu nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omu maka gangye hamwe n'abantu b'omukyanga. Okubaho kwabo hamwe n'okukunda kwabo kuyamba, bimbaasize munonga omu bwire obu bwa bwanyima y'okuzaara, okumpeereza obuhwezi bw'emirimo hamwe n'omu nyehurira.",
            "Eego, mbaasize kuhuumura kurungi kuruga obu nazaara, okukira munonga ahabw'okuba nyine abantu abarikumpwera aha mirimo etari emwe n'emwe, ekirikunyikiriza kuhuumura munonga okukira oku nakubiire ntabaine.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikukira kwerarikirira. N'obu haraabe hariho empindahinduka ezishemereire kukorwa ahabw'omwana w'omwereere, nimpurira nyine obucureera kandi nyeteekateekire kukora ebintu mpora mpora.",
            "Tihariho engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza yenyini ei ndikukuratira omu magara gangye aga buriizooba nainga aha bikwatiraine n'okwereeberera ahanyima y'okuzaara. Enkora yangye etwire neeta omutima aha magara marungi n'obuhabuzi bw'eby'amagara.",
            "Ninkora aha oburemeezi obwo ndikugamba na banywani bangye. N'ensibuko y'amaani y'obuhwezi aha nyehurira kandi okubagana ebiteekateeko byangye n'enyehurira zangye nikimpwera kutahwa amaani n'okugira enteekateeka nungi aha bintu.",
            "Tihariho obu ndikukoresa omubazi gw'enzaarwa. Omuringo gwangye gutwire nigugyenderera amagara marungi n'okukuratira obuhabuzi bw'abakugu omu by'amagara omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, mbaasize kukwatanisa kurungi n'omwana wangye kandi nikinshemeza munonga. Enkoragana egi erikweyongyera n'ekicweka ky'omutaano eky'okuba maama kandi obwire obu nimbutwara nk'obw'omuhendo.",
            "Ngaaha tinyine ebibuuzo nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye obwahati. Nimpurira gye kandi nyeteekateekire aha kukira kwangye n'ebyetaago by'omwana. Ku haakubaho ekintu kyona, ninyija kuronda obuhabuzi bw'abashaho.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa, ninkunda okugyenda n'abanywani bangye buri bu ndikuba nyine akaire. N'obu obwire bw'okuhuumuraho burikuba buri bukye n'omwana w'omwereere, okukorengana n'abandi nikimpwera kuhurira mpuumurizibwe kandi nyine akakwate n'abandi.",
            "Nimpurira gye omu mubiri obwo ndikukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ninyereeberera ndi kurabira omu kugyezaho kurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa n'okuhuumura kurungi n'obu okusherura obwire bw'okwereeberera kurungi kirikubaasa kuba ekyoburemeezi ahabw'omwereere.",
            "Tihariho enyikiriza n'emitwarize omu kicweka kyangye erikwija omu biteekateeko byangye ahanyima y'okuzaara n'okureeberera abaana ebi ndikumanya omu bwire obu.",
            "Tihariho engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa nainga enyikiriza ei ndikukuratira. Enkora yangye neekira kwegamira aha bintu ebi ndikukunda hamwe n'obuhabuzi obw'omutaano, okukira eby'obuhangwa.",
            "Obwahati, tinyine kibuuzo nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye. Nimpurira gye kandi ninfayo munonga aha kukira kwangye n'omwana. Ku haakubaho empindahinduka, ninyija kuronda obuhabuzi bw'abashaho.",
            "Tihariho obu ndikukoresa omubazi gw'enzaarwa. Omuringo gwangye gutwire nigugyenderera amagara marungi n'okukuratira obuhabuzi bw'abakugu omu by'amagara omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, nyine obusaasi aha kironda ahanyima y'okuzaara. Oburemeezi obu n'ekintu eki ndikugumisiriza nk'ekicweka ky'okukira kwangye bwanyima y'okuzaara kandi nyine amatsiko ngu nikiija kubagye obu ndikugumizamu n'okukira.",
            "Obwahati tindikubaasa kwonsya buri kaire nk'oku kirikwetengwa, n'ekirikurugwamu, omwana tarikureebeka nk'orikuhaaga bwanyima y'okwonsa, ekirikunyerarikiriza.",
            " Ndeebire empindahinduka omu kwonka kw'omwana wangye, okukira munonga okukyendeera kw'amashereka omu mabeere gangye, eki n'ekintu eki ndikukyebera ntiireho omuutima okureeba ngu omwana yaatunga eby'okurya ebirikumara.",
            "Tihariho bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire nainga omushwija omuri nyowe hamwe n'omwana wangye. Kwonka nyetegyereize ngu ebigyere n'amaguru by'omwana wangye obumwe nibiba byine obufuki, kandi ninkyegyendesereza kureeba ngu byaba kurungi.",
            "Okubaasa kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, nkagaruka omu irwariro kusherura obuhwezi n'obwegyendesereza kuruga omu bashaho abaabaire bariyo. Nyine amatsiko aha kukira kwangye, nk'oku ndikukuratira obuhabuzi bwabo.",
            "Eego, nyine omugisha gw'okugira obuhwezi omuka kandi maawe ampwereire munonga omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara. Obuhwezi bwe nibumpa obushoboorozi bw'okukora aha byetaago by'omwana owaaheza kuzaarwa kandi obwe ndi kukira.",
            "Eego, obwire obwingi nimbaasa kuhuumura kandi nkabyama kumara eshaaha mwenda buri kiro. Okuhuumura oku n'okw'omugasho munonga omu kukira kwangye kandi nikumpwera kwehurira gye eizooba ryona.",
            "Eego, ntwire nindya kurungi, ndikuta amaani aha by'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa nka ebitookye, ebirikukira kukoresibwa omukyanga eki, hamwe n'ebihimba. Ebyokurya ebi nibihwera omukureeta amaani n'ebiriisa ebirikwetengwa bwanyima y'okuzaara n'omukwonsa.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura kandi okushemererwa ninkunda kuhurikiriza reediyo. N'eky'okushemererwa kyorobi ekirikumpwera kuhumura n'okuruhuukwa okukira munonga omu bwire obu omwana arikuba ahuumwireho.",
            "Nimpurira gye munonga ahabw'okuba maama, n'ekintu ky'omutaano kandi ekirikugararuramu amaani. Obwahati tinyine nshonga nz'omutaano ezirikukwata aha magara gangye nainga amagara g'omwana wangye kandi ninsiima.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikuhurira ngu nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omu maka gangye n'abantu b'omukyanga kyangye. Nkabaasa kugasirwa omu buhwezi bwingi n'okwetegyereza omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara, nk'oku ndikuraba omu buremeezi bw'okuzaara n'okukira.",
            "Eego mbaasize kuhuumura kurungi kuruga obu nazaara ekyabaire kiri eky'omugasho munonga omu kukira kwangye. Okugira obwire bw'okubyama n'okuhuumuraho, nikimpwera kugira amaani n'okureeberera gye omwana wangye.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikukira kwerarikirira. N'obu haraabe hariho empindahinduka omu magara g'omwana owaaheza kuzaarwa, nimpurira nyine obucureera kandi nyeteekateekire kutwara buri eizooba nk'oku ririkwija.",
            "Tihariho engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa nainga enyikiriza ei ndikukuratira ntiireho omutima. Enkora yangye y'okureeberera abakazi ahanyima y'okuzaara hamwe n'okutunga amagara marungi, egumire neeteekateeka munonga aha burungi bwangye hamwe n'obuhabuzi oburikukwata aha magara gangye.",
            "Nintwaza gye oburemeezi obwo ndikugamba na maawe. Naampa obuhwezi bwingi omu nyehurira hamwe n'okwetegyereza kandi nikimpwera munonga kumugambira oku ndikwehurira hamwe n'ebi naarabire omu bwire obu.",
            "Tihariho obu ndikukoresa omubazi gw'enzaarwa. Ekigyendererwa kyangye n'okwerinda n'okukuratira obuhabuzi bw'abakugu omu by'amagara omu bwire obu obw'okutereera bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, mbaasize kugira omukago murungi n'omwana wangye kandi kikandeetera kwehurira gye munonga. Enkoragana egi n'ekicweka kirungi munonga omu kuzaara kandi ninkunda obwire obu turikumara hamwe.",
            "Nyine ebibuuzo ebirikukwata aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'okureeberera omwana wangye kandi nimpurira ngu ebintu biriyo nibigyenda gye nk'oku kibaire nikiteekateekwa.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa, ninkunda kutayaayira banywani bangye obwire bwona naaba nyine obwire. N'obu obwire bw'okuhuumuraho burikuba buri bukye ahabw'omwana w'omwereere, okukorengana n'abandi nikumpwera kwehurira nyine akakwate n'okuhuumuraho kurungi.",
            "Nimpurira gye ahabw'omubiri gwangye ku ndikukizayo bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ninyerinda ndikuhamya ngu nimpuumura ekirikumara kandi ndikurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa, kugira ngu ntungye amagara marungi n'amaani.",
            "Tihariho nyikiriza n'emitwarize omu kicweka kyangye erikukwata ahakuzaara n'okurreeberera omwana ebi ndikumanya hati. Ebintu ebi naarabiremu bitwire biri ebya buri omwe.",
            "Tihariho engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa nainga enyikiriza ei ndikukuratira. Enkora yangye neekira kwegamira aha bintu ebi ndikukunda hamwe n'obuhabuzi obw'omutaano, okukira eby'obuhangwa.",
            "Nimpurira gye munonga ahabw'okuba maama, n'ekintu ekirikunyongyera amaani. Obwahati tinyine nshonga z'omutaano ezirikukwata aha mwoga gwangye nk'omuzaire omusya kandi ninkunda obwire obu.",
            "Ngaaha tinyine ebibuuzo ebirikukwata aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'okureeberera omwana wangye kandi nimpurira ngu ebintu nibigyenda kurungi.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa, ninkunda kutayaayira banywani bangye buri bundikuba nyine obwire burungi. N'obu okusherura obwire bw'okuhuumura kurungi kurikubaasa kuba okw'oburemeezi ahabw'omwana w'omwereere, okutaayaaya oku nikumpwera kwehurira nyine akakwate n'abandi kandi n'empindahinduka nungi.",
            "Nintwaza gye oburemeezi obwo ndikugamba na maama. Naampa obuhwezi bwingi omu nyehurira hamwe n'okwetegyereza ekirikumpwera munonga ku ndikuhurira nyine oburemeezi nainga ku ndikwenda kuhanuura aha kintu. Obuhabuzi bwe buriijo n'obw'omugasho ahariinye.",
            "Tihariho obwahati tindikukoresa omubazi gw'enzaarwa. Omuringo gwangye gw'okukira ahanyima y'okuzaara gutwire nigugyenderera amagara g'abantu boona n'okukuratira obuhabuzi bwona oburikuhebwa abakugu omu by'amagara.",
            "Eego, mbaasize kukwatanisa n'omwana wangye kandi n'enyehurira y'omutaano. Omukago ogu niguguma nigweyongyera buri eizooba kandi nigundeetera okushemererwa n'akamanyiiso k'okuba maama.",
            "Ngaaha tinyine kibuuzo kyona nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'okureeba ngu omwana wangye aine amagara marungi kandi arikureebererwa kurungi.",
            "Nimpurira gye ahabw'omubiri gwangye ku ndikukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ninyereeberera ndikureeba ngu narya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa n'okuhuumura ekirikumara n'obu eki kirikubaasa kuba kigumire n'omwana w'omwereere.",
            "Eego, nimpurira obusaasi bwanyima y'okushemezibwa obu naabire ninzaara. Obusaasi obu n'ekintu eki ndikukoresa nk'ekicweka ky'okukira kwangye kandi nyine amatsiko ngu nikiija kweyongyera omu sande ezirikwija.",
            "Ninyonsa omwana wangye buri shaaha ibiri kandi eego omwana naareebeka nk'orikuhaaga buri bu ari kwonka. Nikingaruramu amaani okureeba ngu naatunga ebiriisa ebi arikwetenga.",
            "Ndeebire empindahinduka omu mwana wangye otwariiremu okwisya n'omuriro (mwingi) gw'ahaiguru. Ndeebire obumanyiso obu kurungi kandi nteekateeka kuronda obuhabuzi bw'abashaho ahonaaho.",
            "Eego, hariho akamanyiso k'omushwija omu mwana wangye, ogurikureebeka ngu n'obutagatsi bw'ahaiguru. Eki n'ekintu ekirikunyerarikiriza munonga kandi ninza kuronda obujanjabi kukikoraho.",
            "Okubaasa kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, ntwire ninza omu eirwariro kukyeberwa n'okukuratira obuhabuzi bw'abashaho abakugu. Nimpurira ndi omumuhanda murungi g'okukira.",
            "Eego nyine obuhwezi omuka kuruga aha mushaija wangye obaire naampwera kuruga obu nazaara. Obuhwezi bwe omu mirimo y'omuka hamwe n'okureeberera omwana, ninyanguhiza omu bwire obu obw'okukira.",
            "Eego, buriijo nimbaasa kuhuumura kandi ningyezaho kubyama haihi eshaaha munaana buri kiro. N'obu kiraabe kitarikugyenda omu maisho omuurundi gumwe ahabw'omwana w'omwereere, obwire obu obw'okuhuumura n'obw'omugasho munonga omu kukira kwangye.",
            "Eego, ntwire nindya kurungi, nkata amaani aha by'okurya ebirimu ebitookye,  ebyokurya eby'omukicweka kyaitu hamwe n'omuceeri,  n'emondi, ebinyoobwa hamwe n'ebihimba, okumpwera kugarura amagara gangye buya n'okunyongyera amaani.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura kandi okushemererwa ninkunda kureeba tiivi. N'omuringo gwangye gw'okuhuumura n'okuruhuukwa okukira munonga omu bwire bw'obucureera obw'omwana yaba agwejegyeire.",
            "Nshemereirwe munonga ahabw'okuba maama, n'eky'okureeberaho ky'okushemererwa. Ninshemererwa munonga ahabw'obuhwezi obu ntungire omu byetaago byangye omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara ekirikutuma mpinduka egi yayanguha.",
            "Eego nimpurira nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omu maka gangye hamwe n'abantu b'omukyanga kyangye. Obuhwezi bwabo n'okwetegyereza bibaire by'omugasho munonga omu bwire obu, ekirikureetera obwire bwa bwanyima y'okuzaara bwabaasika kukorwa kurungi kandi butarikundeetera kwebaganisamu.",
