            "Eego nyine okwerarikirira munonga, okukira munonga ahabw'okwerarikirira okurikukwata aha kugira eby'obugaiga ebitarikumara kureeberera ebyetaago by'eka yaitu erikweyongyera. Eki n'ekintu ky'amaani omu biteekateeko byangye.",
            "Tihariho engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza yenyini ei ndikukuratira omu magara gangye aga buriizooba nainga aha bikwatiraine n'okureeberera abakazi ahanyima y'okuzaara. Enkora yangye etwire neeta omutima aha magara marungi n'obuhabuzi bw'eby'amagara.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikushaba ekirikumpuumuriza n'okumpwera n'okugamba n'abantu abakuzire omu myaka omu kyanga kyangye abarikumpa obwengye n'obuhwezi kurugirira aha bibahikireho.",
            "Tihariho obu ndikukoresa omubazi gw'enzaarwa. Ekigyendereirwa kyangye n'okwerinda n'okukuratira obuhabuzi bw'abakugu omu by'amagara omu bwire obu obw'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye kandi nikihurirwa gye munonga. Enkoragana egi n'ekintu ky'omutaano kandi ekirikwongeramu amaani omu kuzaara kandi ninkunda munonga obwire obu obw'okubanza.",
            "Eego nyine ekibuuzo aha magara gangye. Ntwire nyine puresha kuruga obu nazaara kandi hati nyine omubazi gu ndi kumira. Puresha y'eshagama ku eraabe etari ahansi, nshemereire kugumizamu n'okumira omubazi?",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa ninkunda kureeba tiivi, obwire bwona obu ndikuba nyine. N'obu obwire bw'okushemererwa burikuba buri bukye n'omwana w'omwereere, obwire obu obw'okushemererwa nibumpa obuhuumuriro.",
            "Nimpurira gye omu mubiri ku obu ndikukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ninyerinda kurabira omu kweyonja n'okwejumba omu bisasaizi, nk'okutambura okuruga omuka kuza aha murimo kyaba nikibaasika.",
            "Tindikumanya enyikiriza n'emitwarize y'abantu omu kicweka kyangye aha bikwatiraine n'okureeberera abakazi nainga abaana ahanyima y'okuzaara. Obundi tinkamanyirweho, nainga obundi abantu baitu tibaine migyenzo erikukwata aha nshonga ezi, ezirikumanywa munonga.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikukuratira engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa nainga enyikiriza. Okusharaho kwangye n'ebikorwa byangye nibirugyirira aha kwetegyereza kwangye n'okumanya kwangye okwaburiijo.",
            "Eego, nyine obusaasi bwingi ahabw'okushemezibwa obu naabire ninzaara. Oburemeezi obu n'ekintu eki ndikukoresa nk'ekicweka ky'okukira kwangye bwanyima y'okuzaara kandi nyine amatsiko ngu nibuza kutereera mporampora n'ekironda kiri kukira bwanyima y'obwire.",
            "Ninyonsa omwana wangye emirundi ikumi n'ebiri buri eizooba, kandi nikireebeka ngu omwana naahaaga emirundi mingi bwanyima y'okwonka, ekirikumanyisa ngu aine eby'okurya birungi hamwe n'amashereka.",
            "Ndebire empindahinduka omu kurya kw'omwana wangye, okukira munonga atwiire naatanaka bwanyima y'okwonka. Eki n'ekintu ekirikunyerarikiriza kandi ninteekateeka kuronda obuhabuzi bw'abashaho kumanya ekirikukireeta.",
            "Tihariho bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire nainga omushwija omuri nyowe hamwe n'omwana wangye. Kwonka nyine ebyafaayo by'eizooba rimwe ry'obutabaasa kusheesha eki ndikwenda kukyebera kurungi.",
            "Okubaasa kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, ntwire ninteekateeka aha kukora ebisasaizi ebya makye nk'oku kirikuhaburwa okurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa byona, okubaasa kukira n'okurinda obuyonjo. Nimpurira ndi kweyongyera amaani mporampora.",
            "Tinyine buhwezi bwona omuka obwa hati, kwonka nimbaasa kurwanisa oburemeezi bw'okureeberera omwana owaaheza kuzaarwa n'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, obwo ndikukora enteekateeka y'obwire bwangye n'okwebembeza emirimo yangye nk'oku ndikubasa.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kutunga obwire bw'okuhuumura eizooba ryona, n'obu ndaabe nyine omwana w'omwereere, obwire obu ndikubyama ntiine kutegaanisibwa nibukye. Ningyezaho kuhuumura buri bwanyima y'omwana kubyama, kugira ngu mbaase kukira.",
            "Eego, ningyezaho kurya kurungi kandi eby'okurya byangye birimu ebihimba, ebinyoobwa, enyama, emboga ezindi, obushera hamwe n'ebyenyanja. Nteire omutima aha by'okurya ebi ebirimu ebiriisa, okumpwera okutereera bwanyima y'okuzaara n'okureeba ngu nyine amaani agarikumara.",
            "Eego, obumwe n'obumwe nimpuumura kandi okushemererwa ninkunda kureeba tiivi. N'omuringo gwangye gw'okuhuumura n'okuruhuukwa okukira munonga omu bwire bw'obucureera obu omwana arikuba agwejegyeire nainga arikureebererwa.",
            "Ninyesiimisa munonga okuba maama, n'ekintu ky'omutaano kandi ekirikugaruzamu amaani. Obwahati tinyine nshonga nz'omutaano ezirikukwata aha mwooga gwangye nk'omuzaire omusya kandi ninyikiriza orugyendo oru.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikuhurira nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omuka yangye nainga omu bantu b'omukyanga kyangye. Ninyikiriza ngu nimbaasa kugasirwa omu buhwezi bw'omugasho n'obw'ebiteekateeko omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, mbaasize kutunga okuhuumura okurikumara kuruga obu nazaara, ekireesire amagara gangye n'ebiteekateeko byangye byaba gye. Okugira obwire bw'okubyama n'okuhuumuraho, nikimpwera kwehurira nyine obushoboorozi bw'okureeberera omwana wangye.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikukira kwerarikirira. N'obu haraabe hariho empindahinduka ezishemereire kukorwa ahabw'omwana womwereere, buri izooba nimpurira nyine obucureera.",
            "Ngaaha, tihariho engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza yenyini ei ndikukuratira ntiireho omutima omu magara gangye aga buriizooba nainga aha bikwatiraine n'okwereeberera ahanyima y'okuzaara. Omuringo gwangye gutwire nigugyenderera obuhuumuriza bw'omuntu n'okuhaburwa ahaby'amagara okutwariza hamwe.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikugamba na munywani wangye ou ndikukira kugamba nawe. Okugira omuntu ou naabaasa kugaaniira nawe aha bi ndikuteekateeka  hamwe n'enyehurira zangye, nikimpwera kwehurira nyine obuhwezi omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            " Eego, omubazi gw'enzaarwa gwonka ogu turikukoresa ni eshabiko. Eki n'ekintu ekitwire kiri omu buhangwa bwaitu, kandi nitukishanga kiri eky'omugasho omu bintu ebimwe eby'okureeberera abakazi ahanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye, kandi nikindeetera kwehurira gye munonga. Enkoragana egi erikweyongyera n'ekicweka ky'omutaano kandi ekirikunyongyera amaani ahabwokuba maama, kandi obwire obu nimbutwara nka bukuru.",
            "Eego, nkiriyo nimpurira obusaasi aha kironda ekireetsirwe okushemezibwa ahabw'okuzaara. Nyine oburemeezi, kandi butarikwemerezamu obu ndikuteekateeka ngu nibwija kukyendeera nk'oku ndikugumizamu n'okukira.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kureeba tiivi buri obundikubona obwire bukye. N'obu okushanga obwire burikumara obw'okuhuumuraho, nikibaasa kuba ekizibu n'omwana w'omwereere, obwire bukye obw'okushemererwa nibumpwera okuhuumuraho.",
            "Nimpurira gye ahabw'omubiri gwangye obwo ndikukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ninyerinda kurabira omu kugyezaho kurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa n'okuhuumuraho kurungi, nobu kiraabe kiri kitoorobi ahabw'omwana w'omwereere.",
            "Enyikiriza eya buriijo omu kyanga kyangye n'okuheereza abaana emibazi y'obuhangwa y'okuragurira endwara nyingi. Ogu n'omugyenzo ogurabiirwe kuruga omu busingye n'obusingye, kandi abantu baingi nibeesiga obujanjabi bw'emibazi egi y'enzaarwa aha magara g'abaana baabo.",
            "Eego, enkora y'eby'obuhangwa ei ndikukuratira n'okukoresa yonka n'eshabiko. Ogu n'omucwe gw'abantu omu kyanga kyaitu, kandi ningukuratira nk'omuringo gw'eby'obuhangwa, okukira munonga omu by'okureeberera abakazi ahanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kureeba tiivi buri kundikubona obwire bukye. N'obu okubona obwire burikumara obw'okuhuumuraho, nikibaasa kuba ekizibu ahabw'omwana w'omwereere, obwire bukye bw'okushemererwa obu nibumpwera okuhuumuraho n'okugarukamu amaani.",
            "Eego, omubazi gw'enzaarwa ogu ndikukoresa ni eshabiko. Eki n'ekintu kimwe aha migyenzo yaitu, kandi nikishangwa nk'eky'omugasho aha nshonga ezimwe ez'okwereeberera  ahanyima y'okuzaara hamwe n'okugira amagara marungi.",
            "Eego, nyine obusaasi bukye bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ti bwingi munonga, kwonka n'obusaasi oburikugumaho obu ndikukyendeeza nk'omuringo gw'okugaruka kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Nyine amatsiko ngu nibwiija kweyongyera kukyendeera bwanyima y'obwire.",
            "Ninyonsa omwana wangye ku arikworeka obubonero bw'okwenda konka, n'ahabw'ekyo obwire tiburikushushana eizooba ryona. Okutwarira hamwe nireebeka nk'orikumarwa bwanyima y'okugaburwa, ekirikumpuumuriza.",
            " Ngaaha, tinkareebireho mpindahinduka y'amaani omu kurya kw'omwana wangye nainga oku arikubyama. Nareebeka ariyo nakuratira engyenderwaho y'abaana b'abereere, etarikuhindahinduka omu bwire obu.",
            " Ngaaha, ekirungi, tihariho bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire nainga omushwija omuriinye nainga omwana wangye. Twembi tutwire nitugira obutagasi, kandi titurikworeka obumanyiso oburikworeka ngu twine oburwaire.",
            "Eego, nyine obuhwezi omuka, kandi nshangire nyine kugumizamu nkashaba obuhwezi kuruga ahari ibanyi. N'obu araabe naanyamba, ekyetengo ky'obuhwezi ekirikugyenda omu maisho nikyoreka oburemeezi bw'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara n'okureeberera abaana",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura ekirikumara, kandi ninkoresa omugisha gw'okubyama ku ndikuhurira nduhire. Okuhuumura ekirikumara n'eky'omugasho munonga omu kukira kwangye, n'ahabw'ekyo ninyebembeza okubyama, n'obu kyaba kiri omu bwire bukye.",
            "Eego, ntwire nindya kurungi, kandi eby'okurya byangye birimu emiyembe, ebitakuri, muhogo, ebitookye, enyama hamwe n'emboga ezindi. Nteire amaani aha by'okurya ebi ebirimu ebiriisa, okurinda amagara gangye bwanyima y'okuzaara, n'okureeba ngu nyine amaani agarikumara g'okwonsa n'okukora emirimo yangye eya buriizooba.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura, kandi okushemererwa, ninkunda kutambura kutayaayira banywani bangye bakye. Okukorengana n'abandi nikumpwera kwehurira nyine akakwate n'abandi kandi nikampa akahuumuro kuruga omu mirimo y'obutoosha y'okureeberera n'okukira.",
            "Nimpurira nyine omugisha gw'okuba maama. Obwahati, eki nshemereire kugamba n'okugira ngu okureeberera omwana kuruga aha eizooba ry'okubanza kuhisya obu akuzire, nikibaasa kuba eky'omugasho munonga, nikyetenga okufayo n'okureeberera munonga, kandi ekintebekanisize kukora.",
            "Eego, nimpurira ngu nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omu maka gangye hamwe n'abantu b'omukyanga kyangye. Okubaho kwabo hamwe n'okwenda kwabo kuhwera, bimpwereire munonga omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara, okuheereza obuhwezi omu by'omubiri hamwe n'omu nyehurira, eki ninkisiimira munonga.",
            "Eego, nimpurira mpumwire kurungi kuruga obu nazaara. Okuhuumura ekirikumara n'eky'omugasho ahabw'omubiri gwangye kugaruka omu buteeka kandi nikindeetera kwehurira gye omu bwire obu obw'empinduka.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikukira kwerarikirira. N'obu haraabe hariho empindahinduka ezishemereire kukorwa n'omwana musya, buri izooba nimpurira nyine obucureera.",
            "Eego, hariho engyenderwaho z'obuhangwa nainga enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira. Ebi n'emigyenzo y'omugasho omu kyanga kyaitu, kandi nimbigyenderaho nk'ekicweka ky'obuhangwa bwangye n'okukuzibwa kwangye.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikugamba n'omushaija wangye aha kintu kyona ekirikutureetera oburemeezi. N'oburugo bw'obuhwezi bw'amaani omu nyehurira, kandi okubaasa kumugambira oku ndikwehurira, nikimpwera kugumira gye oburemeezi bwona.",
            "Eego, hariho emibazi y'obuhangwa ei ndikukoresa. Enkora egi etwirweho kuruga omu busingye kuza omu busingye omu byanga byaitu, kandi nshangire eri ey'omugasho omu bintu ebimwe ebirikukwata ahamagara marungi.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye, kandi nikindetera kwehurira nyine amaani. Enkoragana egi n'ekintu ky'omutaano kandi ekirikumaramu amaani omu kuzaara, kandi ninkunda munonga obwire obu obw'okubanza n'omwana wangye.",
            "Ngaaha, tihaine ebi ndikwenda kwebuuza ebirikukwata aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'oburungi bw'omwana wangye, kandi nimpurira ngu ebintu biriyo nibigyenda gye nk'oku kyabaire nikiteekateekwa.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kutambura, obundi n'okutambura kumara obwire bukye nari okutayayira emyanya eri haihi. Eego, ningyezaho okuhuumura obwire bwona obu ndikwehurira nyine ekyetengo, nkatwara obwire obwo okuhuumura n'okugarukamu amaani obwe ndikureeberera omwana.",
            "Obwahati, omubiri gwangye tigurikutunga buremeezi bw'amaani ahabw'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ningyezaho okwerinda ndikukora ebisasaizi omu muringo gwanguhi naaba nyine omugisha, ekirikumpwera kwehurira gye omu mubiri.",
            "Enyikiriza n'emitwarize y'abantu omu kyanga kyangye, erimu okuzibira kweta abazaire baawe eiziina ryabo ery'okubanza, nk'akamanyiso k'ekitiinisa. Okwongyera ahari ekyo, hariho okuta amaani omu kureeberera omushaija waawe, nobu yaakuba akozire enshobi, ekirikworeka omugasho gw'okukwatanisa omu bushwere.",
            "Ngaaha, tihariho migyenzo y'eby'obuhangwa nainga enyikiriza ei ndikukuratira munonga. Enkora yangye neekira kwegamira aha bi ndikukunda hamwe n'obuhabuzi oburikukwata ahabantu boona, omu mwanya gw'okukuratira engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa.",
            "Nimpurira nyine omugisha gw'okuba maama, kandi omu bwire obu, nshemereirwe kugira ngu tinkwerarikirira ahabw'omurimo gwangye nk'omuzaire omusya. Ninshemerererwa obwire obu obw'omutaano.",
            " Ngaaha, tihaine ebi ndikwenda kwebuuza ebirikunyerarikiriza aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye bwanyima y'okuzaara n'okureeba ngu omwana wangye aba aine amagara marungi kandi naareebererwa kurungi. Ku haakubaho empindahinduka, ninyija kuronda obuhabuzi bw'abashaho.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kutamburamu kutayayira banywani bangye ku kirikubaasika. Okwongyera ahari ekyo, obumwe n'obumwe omushaija wangye naantwara aheeru, n'omuringo murungi gw'okuhuumura n'okushemererwa naaba ndi aheeru y'omuka.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikugamba n'omushaija wangye, kandi nitukora kushoboorora obuzibu bwona oburikubaho. Okugira obuhwezi bwe n'okubaasa kugamba nawe omu butunu, nikimpwera kuguma nyine amaani kandi nyine oburemeezi bukye.",
            "Eego, hariho emibazi y'obuhangwa ei ndikukoresa. Enkora egi etwirweho kuruga omu busingye kuza omu busingye omu kyanga kyaitu, kandi ninshanga ngu n'ey'omugasho omu bintu ebimwe ebirikukwata aha magara n'okwereeberera ahanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye, kandi kikandeetera kwehurira nk'omunyamugisha w'amaani kandi kurungi. Enkoragana egi erikweyongyera n'ekicweka ky'omutaano ky'okuhinduka maama, kandi ninkunda munonga obwire obu obw'okubanza.",
            "Ngaaha, tikwo kiri. Tinyine kibuuzo kyona nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye bwanyima y'okuzaara hamwe n'okureeberera omwana wangye, kandi nimpurira ngu ebintu biriyo nibigyenda gye.",
            "Nimpurira orikushusha ng'omubiri gwangye nikiguremeera ahanyima y'okuzaara, kwonka ningyezaho okwereeberera ndi kukora ebisasaizi byanguhi omuka naabona omugisha.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikuhurira busaasi bwingi nainga obutabeerwagye bwanyima y'okuzaara. Nyine amagara marungi omu mubiri, ekirikumpwera kuta amaani omu kureeberera omwereere wangye.",
            "Ninyonsa omwana wangye emirundi nka mushanju buri eizooba. Okutwarira hamwe nikireebeka omwana naahaaga bwanyima y'okugaburwa, ekirikumpumuriza nk'oku ndikuraba omu bwire bwentandikiro y'obuzaire.",
            "Eego, nyetegyereize empindahinduka omu kurya kw'omwana wangye; tarikwenda kwonka munonga nka kare nainga n'omuhimbo nk'okubanza, eki n'ekintu eki ndikukyebera kurungi.",
            "Tihariho bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire nainga omushwija omuriinye hamwe n'omwana wangye. Kwonka, nyetegyereize ngu omwana takyenda kwonka, kandi empinguka egi omu mitwarize ye nenkwataho.",
            "Okubaasa kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, ntwire ninkoresa emibazi y'enzaarwa n'okukuratira engyenderwaho y'obuhangwa eya buriijo omu kyanga kyaitu.",
            "Eego, nyine obuhwezi omuka, kandi n'eky'omugasho omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara. Okuba n'obuhwezi nikinyamba okureeberera omwereere n'okufayo kwereeberera kukira kwangye.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura, n'obu ndaabe nyine omwana w'omwereere, obwire bw'okubyama butarikurabanisibwa nibubaasa kuba bukye. Ningyezaho kukoresa obwire obu omwana arikuba agwejegyeire okuhumuraho.",
            "Eego, ntwire nindya kurungi, kandi ntiire amaani aha by'okurya eby'omukyanga eki ebirimu ebiriisa nka ebitookye n'ebihimba. Ebi nibimpa ebiriisa n'amaani g'omugasho ahanyima y'okuzaara n'okwonsa kyaba nikibasika.",
            "Eego, obumwe n'obumwe nimbaasa kuhuumuraho. Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kumara obwire n'ab'omuka yangye nainga n'okuhurikiza reediyo naaba nyine obwire.",
            "Nimpurira gye ahabw'okuba maama, n'ekintu ky'omutaano kandi ekirikugaruramu amaani. Obwahati, tinyine nshonga nz'omutaano ezirikukwata aha magara gangye nainga amagara g'omwana wangye, eki ndikusiima.",
            "Eego, nimpurira ngu nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omu maka gangye hamwe n'abantu b'omukyanga. Okubaho kwabo hamwe n'okwenda kuhwera kwabo, bimbaasize munonga omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara, okuheereza obuhwezi oburikumara n'obw'ebiteekateeko.",
            "Eego, ntungire okuhuumura okurikumara kuruga obu nazaara, ekyomugasho munonga omu kukira kwangye kwangye. Okugira obwire bw'okubyama n'okuhuumuraho, nikimpwera kugira amaani n'okureeberera gye omwana wangye.",
            "Eego,ninyerarikirira munonga okukira obwa butoosha, okukira munonga ahabw'okwebuuza aha mwana wangye otarikonka kurungi. Eki n'ekintu eki ndikushanga kiri eky'oburemeezi omu bwire obu.",
            "Eego, hariho engyenderwaho z'obuhangwa nainga enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira. Ebi n'emigyenzo y'omugasho omukyanga kyaitu, kandi nimbigyenderaho nk'ekicweka ky'obuhangwa bwangye n'okukuzibwa kwangye, ekirikukwata aha bintu bitari bimwe na bimwe omu magara gangye.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikugamba na maame. Naampa obuhwezi bwingi omu nyehurira hamwe n'okwetegyereza, kandi nikimpwera munonga kumugambira oku ndikwehurira hamwe n'ebi ndikuramu omu bwire obu.",
            " Eego, hariho emibazi y'obuhangwa ei ndikukoresa. Enkora egi etwirweho kuruga omu busingye kuza omu busingye omu kyanga kyaitu, kandi ninshanga ngu n'ey'omugasho omu bintu ebimwe ebirikukwata aha kuba gye n'okukira.",
            "Eego, mbaasize kukwatanisa n'omwana wangye kandi n'enyehurira y'omutaano. Omukago ogu niguguma nigweyongyera buri eizooba, kandi nigundeetera okushemererwa kwingi  akamayiso k'amaani ak'omugasho nk'omukazi omuzaire (nka maama).",
            "Ngaaha, tihaine ebi ndikwenda kwebuuza nainga ebirikukwata aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'okubaho kurungi kw'omwana wangye, kandi nimpurira ngu ebintu biriyo nibigyenda gye nk'oku kyabaire nikiteekateekwa.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkira kuguma omuka, kandi eego,nyine obwire bw'okuhuumura, okukira munonga omwana yaaba agwejegyeire nainga ku naaba nyine obwire bwangye omu eizooba. Obwire obu obw'obucureera nibungaruram amaani.",
            "Nimpurira ngu omubiri gwangye gukiriyo niguhinduka bwanyima y'okuzaara, kandi ninyereeberera kurabira omukugyezaho kurya ebyokurya ebirimu ebiriisa n'okuhuumura kurungi, n'obu kiraabe nikibasa kuba kigumire obumwe n'obumwe ahabw'omwana w'omwereere.",
            "Enyikiriza n'emitwarize y'abantu omu kyanga kyangye, erimu okukoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa omu mirimo y'eby'amagara etari emwe n'emwe, kandi abantu baingi nibeesiga emibazi y'obuhangwa egi kubabaisaho n'okuragurira endwara eza buriijo. Obwengye obu buriijo niburaba omu busingye buza omu bundi.",
            "Eego, hariho eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira. Eby'obuhangwa ebi n'eby'omugasho omu kicweka kyaitu kandi n'ekicweka ky'okukuzibwa kwangye hamwe n'obuhangwa bwangye, n'omuringo ogu ndikukoresa ebintu bitari bimwe na bimwe omu magara gangye, otwariiremu n'okwereeberera ahanyima y'okuzaara.",
