            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkira kuguma omuka,kandi eego,nyine obwire bw'okuhuumura, okukira munonga omu bwire obu omwana arikubyamaho nainga obu ndikubaasa kusherura obwire bw'obucureera. Obwire obu nibumpwera kugarukamu amaani.",
