            "Nimpurira ngu omubiri gwangye guriyo nigugaruka omu buringaaniza bwanyima y'okuzaara, kandi ninyereeberera kurabira omu kugyezaho kurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa n'okuhuumura kurungi, ekirikubaasika, ekirikuba kiri eky'omugasho omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, nyine obusaasi n'obutabererwa gye bwanyima y'okuzaara. Eki n'ekicweka ky'okutereera bwanyima y'okuzaara, kandi ninkikora kurungi nk'oku ndikubasa, obwo ndikureeberera omwana wangye w'omwereere.",
            "Ninyonsa omwana wangye emirundi mingi eizooba ryona, kandi eego, okutwarira hamwe nikireebeka ngu omwana naiguta bwanyima y'okwonka, ekirikumpumuriza.",
            "Eego, ntwire nindeeba empindahinduka omu kurya n'okubyama kw'omwana wangye kuruga obu yazaarwa. Empindahinduka ezi n'eza buriijo omu bereere, kandi ninyega kwetegyereza n'okukoragana n'ebyetengo ebirikweyongyera.",
            "Ngaaha, n'ekirungi, tihariho bubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire nainga omushwija omuriinye nainga omwana wangye. Twembi tutwire nitugira obutagasi, kandi titurikworeka bubonero oburikworeka ngu twine oburwaire.",
            "Kubaasa kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, ntwire ninyejaburira, ekikorwa ky'obuhangwa omu kyanga kyaitu. Nimpurira ngu kiriyo nikimpwera omu kukira kwangye.",
            "Nyineho obuhwezi omuka, kandi obumwe n'obumwe ninkora emirimo yangye nshutami, okurinda amaani n'okwikiriza omubiri gwangye kugarurwa busya. Eki nikimpwera kutereeza obujunanizibwa bwangye n'ebyetaago byangye bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, nimbaasa kuhuumura, kwonka eky'obusaasi, tindikubyama ekirikumara, ekirikubaasa kuba eky'oburemeezi aha bazaire ahab'okuba n'omwereere. Ningyezaho kuhuumura buri murundi ogu omwana agwejegyeire okubaasa kuruhuukwa.",
            "Eego, ntwire nindya kurungi, kandi eby'okurya ebirikuba biriho n'obushera, oburimu ebiriisa kandi oburikwetengwa bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ningyezaho kurya eby'okurya ebindi ebirimu ebirikubaasa kureeta amagara marungi.",
            "Eego, obumwe n'obumwe ninkihuumura, kandi okushemererwa, ninkunda kureeba tiivi. N'omuringo gw'okuhuumura n'okuruhuuka, namunonga omu bwire bw'obucureera obu omwana arikuba abyami.",
            "Nimpurira gye ahabw'okuba maama, n'ekintu kirungi munonga. Ekiri kunyerarikiriza n'ekyetengo ky'okwongyera aha bashaho omu marwariro g'omubyaro, okubaasa kuhwera abakazi abato (abarikuzaara omurundi gw'okubanza) n'abaana b'abereere omu byanga byaitu.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikuhurira ngu nyine obuhwezi burikumara kuruga omu maka gangye nainga abantu b'omukyanga kyangye. Ninyikiriza ngu nimbaasa kugasirwa omu buhwezi n'okwetegyereza omu bwire obu bwanyima y'okuzaara, nk'oku ndikuraba omu buremeezi bw'okuzaara n'okukira.",
            " Ngaaha, tindikubaasa kuhuumura kurungi kuruga obu nazaara, ekireesireho oburemeezi bwingi bwanyima y'okuzaara, nk'oku ndikugyezaho kukira n'okureeberera omwana w'omwereere n'oturo twempime.",
            "Ngaaha, tindikukira kwerarikirira. N'obu haraabe hariho empindahinduka ezirikureetwa omwana w'omwereere, buri izooba nimpurira nyine obucureera.",
            "Eego, hariho eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira. Eby'obuhangwa ebi n'eby'omugasho omu kicweka kyaitu kandi n'ekicweka ky'okukuzibwa kwangye hamwe n'obuhangwa bwangye, n'omuringo ogu ndikukoresa ebintu bitari bimwe na bimwe omu magara gangye, otwariiremu okureeberera abakazi ahanyima y'okuzaara hamwe n'okugira amagara marungi.",
            "Obumwe n'obumwe ninyegyendesereza oburemeezi obwo ndikuhunama nkateekateeka. Eego, nyine abantu abu ndikubaasa kugamba nabo ku ndikuhurira nyine okureemererwa kw'amaani, ekirikumpwera kurinda ebiteekateeko byangye n'okutunga obuhwezi omu bwire bw'oburemeezi.",
            "Eego, hariho emibazi y'enzaarwa ei ndikukoresa, okukira munonga ey'obuhangwa. Ebi bitwire nibikozesibwa omu bantu baitu kumara obwire buraingwa, kandi ninyikiriza ngu biine emigasho aha magara n'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye, kandi nikindeetera kwehurira gye omu nyehurira. Enkoragana egi erikweyongyera n'ekicweka ky'omutaano eky'okuba maama, kandi ninkunda munonga obwire obu obw'okubanza.",
            "Tihariho eki ndikwenda kwebuuza nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'okureeberera omwana wangye, kandi nimpurira ngu ebintu byona biri gye.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ningyezaho kukora ebisasaizi by'omubiri buri naaba nyine obwire. N'obu okusherura obwire bw'okuhuumura kurungi kurikubaasa kuguma ahabw'omwana w'omwerere, obwire bukye obw'okukora emirimo y'omubiri nibumpwera kwehurira gye.",
            "Nimpurira ngu okurinda obuyonjo n'eky'omugasho aha mubiri gwangye, namunonga omu bwire bw'okuzaara. Ninyerinda kurabira omu kuguma nyine obuyonjo, ekirikuhwera omubiri gwangye kuba gye n'okukira.",
            "Eego, hariho enyikiriza hamwe n'emitwarize omu kyanga kyangye aha bikwatiraine n'okureeberera abaana ahanyima y'okuzaara hamwe n'okureebererera abaana. Eby'obuhangwa ebi nibikira kurabira omu maka, kandi nibikwata aha muringo ogu turikukoramu ebintu bitari bimwe na bimwe ebirikukwata aha bazaire abasya.",
            "Eego, hariho eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza ezi ndikukuratira. Eby'obuhangwa ebi n'eby'omugasho omu kicweka kyaitu kandi n'ekicweka ky'okukuzibwa kwangye hamwe n'obuhangwa bwangye, n'omuringo ogu ndikukoresa ebintu bitari bimwe na bimwe omu magara gangye, otwariiremu n'okureeberera abakazi baabo ahanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Nimpurira gye ahabw'okuba maama burizooba, nkamanya omurimo gwangye omutsya. Obwahati, tinyine nshonga nz'omutaano ezirikukwata ahaburugo bwangye nk'omuzaire omusya, kandi ninkiriza orugyendo oru.",
            "Ngaaha, tihaine ebi ndikwenda kwebuuza nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'okubaho kurungi kw'omwana wangye, kandi nimpurira ngu ebintu biriyo nibigyenda gye nk'oku kyabaire nikiteekateekwa.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa,ninkunda kureeba tiivi buri bwanyima y'obwire bukye. N'obu okushanga obwire burikumara obw'okuhuumuraho, nikibaasa kuba ekizibu n'omwana musya, obwire bukye obw'okushemererwa nibumpwera okuhuumuraho.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi obwo ndikugyezaho kukora ebisasaizi obu naaba nyine obwire. N'obu obwire bw'okukora ebisasaizi by'amaani burikuba buri bukye n'omwana omwereere, n'obwire bukye bw'okukora ebisasaizi aha mubiri nibimpwera kwehurira gye.",
            "Eego, hariho emibazi y'obuhangwa ei ndikukoresa. Obu n'oburyo obwahinguzibwe kuruga omu busingye kuza omu busingye omu kyanga kyaitu, kandi nibureebeka nk'obw'omugasho omu bintu ebimwe ebirikukwata aha kuba gye n'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye, kandi nikindeetera kwehurira gye omu nyehurira. Enkoragana egi erikweyongyera n'ekicweka ky'omutaano eky'okuba maama, kandi ninkunda munonga obwire obu obw'okubanza n'omwana wangye.",
            "Ngaaha, tinyine bibuuzo ebirikukwata aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye n'okureeba ngu omwana wangye aba aine amagara marungi kandi arikureebererwa kurungi.",
            "Okukoresa gye eby'obuyonjo n'okurya eby'amagara marungi. ebyokurya nk'amate, enyama, amahuri n'ebindi",
            "Okurwanisa obusaasi n'eky'omugasho munonga. Ninkoresa ebyoma ebirikwotsya omubiri, ninkora eby'okukoresa omubiri, ninywa amaizi maingi, okwenyiga n'amaizi gari kutagata n'okusiiga ebicweka ebirikuteganisiibwa",
            "Nkabaasa kuhikaana na tiimu z'eby'amagara omu kyaro. Eki kukirikuba kitarikuhwera, nkaza omu irwariro eriri haihi.",
            "Okurinda obuyonjo, okwetantara okukwatwa akakooko ka muzibwe, okwetantara okukora emirimo mingi erikubaasa kutaho oburemeezi bw'ekironda aha magara gaawe.",
            "Obubonero bw'oburwaire ni obutagasi bw'omubiri, obusaasi bw'amaani omu nda, okuguruka kw'amaizi kuruga omu bakazi, n'oburwaire bw'omubiri. Omuringo gw'okuzibira n'okureeba ngu naamira emibazi kurungi nk'oku omushaho wangye yaangambiire.",
            "Eki nikibaasa kukorwa kurabira omu kukora enteekateeka y'emirimo yangye y'obutoosha otwariiremu n'okuhuumura okushemereire kujanjaara eizooba ryona.",
            "Nyine kutayayira eirwariro eriri haihi okushwijumwa n'okuragurirwa omushaho otendekirwe.",
            "Okutayayira eirwariro eriri haihi n'eky'omugasho munonga. Kwonka, nkaba ninteekateeka aha mpindahinduka y'omubiri nka obutagasi, obusaasi, okuruga eshagama n'okuzimba ebicweka by'omubiri",
            "Eego, omucwe gw'enzaarwa ogurikubaasa kuhwera okuragurirwa bwanyima y'okuzaara n'okukoresa obukooko oburikutagata. Enkora egi neebaasa kuhwera omu kukyendeeza oburemeezi, okureetaho entambura y'eshagama, n'okugarura busya amagara g'omuntu ahanyima y'okuzaara",
            "Ninywa amaizi maingi, nyonka omwana obutoosha kwenda kwongyera amashereka agarikuruga omunda, nindya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa byona, n'okwetantara okwerarikirira.",
            "OBUZITO BW'OKUKYENDEERA: 1. Kyendeeza emirimo etari y'obutoosha 2. Rya ebyokurya ebirimu ebiriisa byona 3. Rya ebijuma bingi OKUTEEKATEEKA OBUREMEEZI: 1. Yongyera amaani omu kukora eby'emizaano, kurya eby'okurya ebitarimu kalori nyingi nk'emboga.",
            "1. okuhindura paadi z'abaana buri kaire 2. Okunaaba engaro buri kaire 3. Okurya ebyokurya birungi 4. Okunaaba buri kaire 4. Okujwara emyenda erikwera",
            "Nindonda abanywani n'abantu b'omuka abu ndikuhurizana nabo oburemeezi bwangye buri kaire.",
            "Bagana n'abanywani abaine obwesigae hamwe n'ab'omuka yaawe, kweta bataahi baawe omu mirimo y'abaana baawe, za omu irwariro eriri haihi",
            "Okuhuumura ekirikumara, okuza kukyeberwa omu eirwariro, n'okweshweka/okwefubika ebirikumara.",
            "Eego, Nkabaasa kuhabura okukora ebisasaizi (kegel), hamwe n'okwenyigisa n'amaizi gari kutagata.",
            "Nkaba ninza kutoorana eby'okurya by'emihendo y'ahansi. Nkaba nkoresa n'omusiri gwangye oguri enyima y'eka.",
            "1. Okugira obusaasi bwingi 2. Okweyongyera kwa puresha 3. Okutahumura gye kw'omubiri 4. omushwija n'okufukiirirwa",
            "Ku oraabe otarikubaasa kutayayira eirwariro ahabw'oburemeezi bwanyima y'okuzaara kandi otarikwetegyereza oku orikubaasa kubukoresa, nikibaasa kuba eky'omugasho kusherura obuhabuzi kuruga omu bantu abarikwesigwa, nk'abakuru nainga tiimu y'eby'amagara ey'omubyaro, abarikubaasa kuba nibamanya emibazi Kyaba nikibaasika, teeraho kuhikaana n'omushaho orikukoresa esimu kutunga obuhabuzi.",
            "Eego; Okukora ebisasayizi, Okunywa amaizi garikwotsya, Okutambura",
            "Okumanyisa ab'omuka yaawe, aba VHT hamwe n'ab'obushoborozi b'omubyaro abarikubaasa kukuhwera kutunga obujanjabi.",
            "Hariho okukoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa okwanguhiza okuzaara",
            "Nyowe tihaine eki ndikukuratira, kwonka mpuriire banywani bangye abarikuhamya ngu abaana nibahebwa amaziina ga baishe na baishenkuru.",
            "Nimpurira gye ahabw'okuba maama. Ekirikunyerarikiriza munonga n'okbutabyama nyekiro ahabw'okurira kw'omwana. Eki kiteganiise amagara gangye.",
            "Ngaaha, tihaine eki ndikwenda kubuuza ebikwatiraine n'amagara gangye obwahati. Nimpurira gye kandi nyeteekateekire aha kukira kwangye n'okureeberera omwana aha omu Uganda.",
            "Ninkunda kuzaana SODUKU aha simu yangye. Nindeeba n'obutambi bwa vidiyo bwa Tiktok.",
            "Eego, buriijo ningamba na mugyenzi wangye. Omu by'okureeberera oburemeezi,ninkora ebintu ebirikunshemeza nka okuzaana emizaano aha simu n'okureeba vidiyo za tiktok",
            "Eego, niinyiga omubiri n'amaizi garikwosya, okunaabisa omwana wangye omu  y'obuhangwa erikwetwa shabiko.",
            "Eego, nkaine. Nimpurira gye munonga ahabwokuba nikigaruramu amaani",
            "Ngaaha, tikwo kiri. Tinyine bibuuzo ebirikukwata aha magara gangye obwahati. Ninteekateeka aha kukira kwangye bwanyima y'okuzaara hamwe n'omwana wangye orikubaasa kuba omushaho omu biro by'omumaisho.",
            "Nimpurira gye omu mubiri gwangye. Ninyeyongyera kutereera  kandi kurungi.",
            "Okunywa amaizi maingi okwongyera amaizi omu mubiri gwawe, n'okwenyiga n'ebirikwosya emirundi eshatu buri eizooba, nikibaasa kutuubya obusaasi",
            "Nkasherura eirwariro eriri haihi nsherura obujanjabi kuruga aha bashaho abatendekirwe. Nimbaasa n'okusherura aha mikutu ya intaneeti",
            "Kozesa amaizi garikutagata n'omwonyo okunaaba ekironda ekyetooroire ehuuzi. Nikirungi okunaaba n'omwonyo",
            "Obubonero burimu: Obusaasi n'obutashemererwa, omushwija, okujwa amahira n'eshagama. Oku barikubaasa kuzibira: Okugumizamu n'eby'obuyonjo, okurya kurungi, okukora ebisasaizi n'okunywa emibazi",
            "1. N'okukora emirimo mikye, kyaba nikibaasika,  kandi oshutama. 2. Okumira emibazi y'obusaasi. 3. Rya ebyokurya ebiine ebiriisa byona",
            "Nkamanyisa abanyabuzaare bangye ab'ahamara, okukoresa za paadi. . Kandi oburemeezi bw'okujwa eshagama ku burikugumizamu buri bwingi munonga, kuhindura paadi emirundi 3 omu shaaha emwe nainga nokurengaho, nkaaza omu eirwariro eriri haihi ahonaaho.",
            "Kyebera eshagama ei orikushohoza orikukyebera n'okubara omuhendo gwa paadi z'orikukoresa. Zitahingura ishatu omu eizooba rimwe. Kyebera obusaasi kandi ku burikuguma nibweyongyera, za ah'eirwariro eriri haihi ahonaaho.",
            "Eego. Okuha omukazi omuzaire eby'okurya ebiine ebiriisa ebirikumara, emboga hamwe n'ebihimba. Eki nikitwariramu obushera, enyama, shukaari. Ebindi ebirikubaasa kukorwa, n'okwenyiga n'edeere omu maizi gari kwosya.",
            "Omuzaire naahigwa kurya eby'okurya ebirikwotsya, ebirimu esupu erikumara hamwe n'ekikopo kye kirikotsa kandi kirimu shukaari aha muringo ogurikwotsya buri hanyima y'okurya emirundi 3 buri eizooba",
            "Okubyamisa buri kaire, okukora ebisasaizi, okukyendeeza aha shukaari, okukora emirimo y'omuka, okukyendeeza eby'okurya ebirimu ebishaju, n'eky'ahamuheru, okurya eby'okurya ebitarimu kabohaidreti nk'obuhunga.",
            "N'okuhindura paadi obutoosha, okushara enza buri sande, okwozya ebijwaro buri kaire, n'okunaaba emirundi ebiri buri eizooba.",
            "Okurya kurungi n'okunywa amaizi maingi, okuhuumura ekirikumara, waaba oine obusaasi, mira emibazi y'obusaasi. Obumanyiso ku buragumizemu, za ah'eirwariro erikuri haihi.",
            "Hikirira munywani waawe nainga omunyabuzaare waawe ow'ahamara, za aha muhumuriza, shaba obuhwezi kuruga omu myanya y'ediini nk'ekanisa, za omu eirwariro eri haihi.",
            "Okunywa amaizi maingi, okuhuumura munonga, okumira emibazi y'obusaasi, n'okuteekaho ebyeshweko ebirikumara. Obubonero nk'obwo ku burikugumizamu, za omu eirwariro eriri haihi.",
            "Eego, ebisasaizi by'omu bubero n'enyugunyu, nk'oku rotama, okukwata enkari waaba noosheesha.  okutagirekura kugyenda juba.",
            "Okurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa (ebihimba, ebinyoobwa, soya), eby'okurya ebirikwera (oburo, ebicoori) nainga ebirikuribwa emizi (emondi, ebitakuri) nainga ebitookye",
            "Okujwa eshagama kw'amaani okurikubaasa kureebeka omu kuhindura paadi ezirikuhingura emirundi eshatu buri izooba, obusaasi bw'omunda, omushwija n'okushwekyerera, okushaasha omutwe, okushekyerera n'okusesema, okureeba kubi nainga okufeerwa amaisho, okuroga kubi.",
            "Okunywa ebirikwotsya, okunyiga enda n'endeere (ebirikosa) hamwe n'okunywa enkoombe (obushera bw'oburo) bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego: 1. eby'okurya by'enzaarwa ebitebeekanisiibwe kurungi, nimbirya birikwotsya nainga birikufuka. Okwenyiga n'amaizi garikwosya n'endeere 3. Okunywa enkoombe (obushera bw'oburo) bwanyima y'okuzaara",
            "Nimanyisa abanyabuzaare, abebembezi b'ekigombe kya VHT, abebembezi b'ekanisa kandi kyaba nikibaasika, nimanyisa omushaho.",
            "Okukoresa eby'obuhangwa okunaaba, okurya n'okunywa",
            "Ngaaha, tindikugyendera kimwe aha migyenzo y'eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza. Omuringo gwangye nigwegamira ebyenda byangye n'obwengye bwangye okukira okukuratira eby'obuhangwa aha omu Uganda.",
            "Nimpurira gye munonga ahabw'okuba maama, n'ekintu kirungi munonga aha omu Uganda. Kwonka, ekindi kutiina munonga n'ekiteekateeko ky'okufeerwa omwana ahanyima y'okuzaara, ekirikunyerarikiriza munonga.",
            "Ngaaha, tinyine bibuuzo ebirikukwata aha magara gangye obwahati omu Uganda. Ninteekateeka munonga aha magara gangye n'okureeberera omwana wangye, kandi nimpurira ngu ebintu nibigyenda gye.",
            "Eego, nyine obwire bw'okuhuumuraho aha omu Uganda, kandi okushemererwa, ninkunda kureeba obuzaano bwa tiivi, okuza aha TikTok, okugamba na banywani bangye, n'okwejumba omu bisasaizi b'omubiri kubaasa kuguma nyine amaani kandi n'okushemererwa.",
            "Ninkora aha buremeezi ndi kurabira omu bintu bitari bimwe na bimwe omu Uganda, otwariiremu okuhurikiriza ebyeshongoro byomwihanga, okureeba tiivi, okugamba na banywani bangye, n'okwejumba omu bisasaizi okumpwera kutereeza ebiteekateeko byangye n'okwehurira gye.",
            "Eego, enkora y'obuhangwa ei ndikukoresa aha omu Uganda n'omuringo gw'obuhangwa ogw'okuteeka ebyokurya, nk'okuteeka n'okukoomeera ebitookye omu ndeere. Ogu n'omuringo ogurikukoresibwa munonga omu buhangwa bwaitu, kandi ninsiima oburungi n'omuringo gw'okukoresa.",
            "Eego, ntungire akakwate n'omwana wangye omuri Uganda, kandi ninyehurira kurungi munonga, okukira munonga omu bwire bw'okwonsa. Obwiire obwo obw'okushemererera hamwe, nibureetaho okukwatanisa kw'amaani ahagati yaitu, eki ninkunda munonga.",
            "Ngaaha, tinyine kibuuzo kyona ekirikukwata aha magara gangye omubwiire obu omuri Yuganda. Nimpurira gye kandi nyeteekateekire aha kukira kwangye hamwe n'omwana wangye.",
            "1. Ninkunda omubiri gwangye. Nkigaburira eby'okurya ebirimu ekiriisa ky'omubiri n'emboga 3. Ninkuratira obuyonjo, nk'okunaaba buri kaire, okwozya ebijwaro buri kaire 4. Nyine okubyama okurikumara. Obumwe n'obumwe ninkora ebisasaizi.",
            "Okushemeza omubiri, okuhuumura ekirikumara, okunywa amaizi garikutagata",
            "Okunaaba ekironda n'amaizi ag'omwonyo garikwotsya, n'okunaaba n'esabuuni y'okwozya. Kandi obumanyiso ku burikugumizamu, za aha eirwariro eriri haihi.",
            "Ziboneze n'amaizi marungi ag'omwonyo, hindura paadi emirundi eshatu nari ena buri izooba.",
            "Obubonero : Omushwija n'okushwekyerera, obusaasi omu nda-nto, okuruga omunda kw'amaizi, okubura kwenda eby'okurya, okureebeka nk'orikurwara.",
            "Hika aha banyabuzaare, obundi obashabe kutuura nabo, gezaho kukora oshutami, okurwanisa obusaasi, okurya kurungi funa amaani, teekaho obwire bw'okuhuumura",
            "Kora ebisasayizi bikye, nywa emibazi erikuhaburwa, nywa amaizi maingi",
            "Gyeza aha nda okureeba yaaba eigufa rikyendeire, reeba yaaba eshagama eriyo nekyendeera orikukyebera omuhendo gwa paadi ekirikwetengwa buri eizooba ",
            "Eego: Amaizi ag'omwonyo ag'obufuki, okugyemesereza n'amaizi ag'obufuki orikukoresa amababi g'ebitookye",
            "Nywa ekikopo ky'obushera oburimu amate, soya nainga enjuma ezindi (z'ebyokurya) buri shaaha ina. Okwenyiga n'amaizi garikoosya hamwe n'endeere.",
            "N'okurya ebyokurya birungi, n'okukora ebisasaizi buri kaire",
            "Okunaaba butoosha, okuhindura paadi, okunaaba omungaro otakakwatsire n'ahanyima y'okukwata aha mwana",
            "Okugamba n'omunywani wangye ow'ahamara ahaburemeezi obu ndikutunga, okushoma baiburi, okuzina ebyeshongoro by'ediini",
            "Orikusherura obujanjabi ahonaaho",
            "Okukoresa emibazi y'obusaasi nka paracintamol, n'okuhuumura kurungi.",
            "Eego, ebisasaizi bya Kegel nibihaburwa munonga ahabw'okugaruka kubagye bwanyima y'okuzaara kandi nibibaasa kukorerwa omuka omuri Uganda. Ebisasaizi ebi nibihwera omu kwongyera amaani omu nyama z'amatako ezirikubaasa kuba zireegukire omu bwire bw'okuzaara.",
            "Okureeba ngu wakoresa eby'okurya ebirikuba biriho omu Uganda, okoresa eby'okurya ebirikuba biriho omu muringo ogurikworeka ngu wakoresa eby'okurya ebirimu ekiriisa, hamwe n'ebijuma n'emboga ebirikuba biriho.",
            "Obubonero oburikworeka ngu oshemereire kuronda obujanjabi ahonaaho bwanyima y'okuzaara omuri Yuganda, harimu okujwa eshagama nyingi erimu obuturugunyu, okwerarikirira, n'omushwija, nainga omwana yaaba atarikubaasa kwonkya.",
            "Ku oraabe otarikubaasa kuza omu eirwariro omu Uganda, noobaasa kurwanisa oburemeezi bwanyima y'okuzaara orikukora emirimo etari y'amaani n'okwejumba omu mirimo erikubaasa kukureetera kugira ebi wakora, nk'okuza omu nteekateeka z'ekanisa nainga emikoro endiijo.",
            "Eego, hariho emicwe y'obuhangwa omu Uganda erikubaasa kuhwera omukukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, nk'okunywa emibazi y'obuhangwa nka emumbwa hamwe n'okukoresa ebyoma by'omubiri ebirikwosya, okukyendeeza oburemeezi n'okukira.",
            "Ku oraabe oine oburemeezi kandi otarikubaasa kuza omu eirwariro omuri Yuganda, ahabw'okujwa eshagama nyingi, gezaho okwonsa obwire buraingwa, okureebeka ngu nyinenda yahooka, kandi ahabw'omushwija, noobaasa kumira emibazi y'obusaasi nka paracetamol yaaba eriho.",
            "Enyikiriza n'emitwarize y'abantu b'omu kicweka kyangye omuri Uganda, erimu okunywa emibazi y'obuhangwa okurahusa ebisha by'okuzaara, kandi abantu abamwe nibaikiriza okunywa amaarwa g'omwihanga (waragi) n'ekigyendererwa ky'okuzaara omwana oshemeire.",
            "Eego, ninkuratira emicwe y'eby'obuhangwa hamwe n'enyikiriza aha omu Uganda, nk'ezo ezirikugambwaho ahaiguru ezirikukwata aha mibazi y'okuzaara hamwe n'enyikiriza y'okunywa amaarwa (waragi) omu bwire bw'okuzaara, ahabw'okuba ebi n'eby'obuhangwa bwaitu.",
            "Ninyesiimisa munonga okuba maama aha omu Uganda. Nikireebeka nyine okwerarikirira okw'omurundi ogu ahabw'omurimo gwangye nk'omuzaire omusya, kandi ninyiriza omwooga ogu.",
            "Obundi, okureeba ngu nyine enkoju itaano kuruga omu kuzaara aha omu Uganda, ekibuuzo kyangye n'okumanya yaaba nikiba kitaine nshonga kugaruka kutwara enda omu biro by'omumaisho. Eku nik'okwerarikirira oku nyine.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa aha omu Uganda, ninkunda kumara obwire bwangye mpurikirize ebyeshongoro by'ediini, ebirikumpuumuriza, hamwe n'okutambura omu mwebazyo obu naaba nyine omugisha.",
            "Eego, ninkora aha kwerarikirira aha omu Uganda ndikukoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa erikukorwa omu bintu by'obuhangwa. Ogu nigwo muringo gw'obuhangwa gwangye gw'okumaraho oburemeezi, kandi n'ekintu eki nyegire omu kyanga kyangye.",
            "Eego,ninkoresa emibazi y'enzaarwa omu Uganda. Nimpurira nyine ekitiinisa n'okushemererwa okuta enkora y'eby'obuhangwa omu magara gangye, ahabw'okuba n'ekicweka kikuru ky'obuhangwa bwaitu kandi buriijo nikihuumuriza.",
            "Ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye omuri Uganda, kandi ninyehurira gye munonga. Kwonka, okwerarikirira kwangye okunyine obwahati nikukwata aha nkojo  itaano ezi naabaire nyine enyima hamwe n'oku zirikubaasa kuteganisa enda zangye ez'omumaisho.",
            "Ninyesiimisa amagara gangye aha omu Uganda. Ninyerinda kurabira omu okunaaba buri kaire, okureebeka ngu nyine obuyonjo, okurya eby'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa byona, n'okukora ebisasaizi buri kaire, kyaba nikibaasika.",
            "Ku oraabe otungire oburemeezi bw'okukira bwanyima y'okusharamu kandi hatariho by'okukoresa omu Uganda, n'eky'omugasho kuguma oine obuyonjo omu mwanya ogwakuteerwaho n'okugamba n'abashaho waaba oine obubonero bw'amaani.",
            "Ku oraabe otari haihi n'eirwariro omuri Yuganda kandi orikwetenga okureeberera emishono n'amaziga bwanyima y'okuzaara, oshemereire kuboneza gye omwanya n'amaizi garikutagata kandi marungi, oyetantare okukora emirimo y'amaani erikubaasa kuremesa emibiri yaawe.",
            "u oraabe otari haihi n'eirwariro omuri Yuganda kandi orikwetenga okureeberera emishono n'amaziga bwanyima y'okuzaara, oshemereire kuboneza gye omwanya n'amaizi garikutagata kandi marungi, oyetantare okukora emirimo y'amaani erikubaasa kuremesa emibiri yaawe. (36 ebigambo)",
            "Obubonero bw'okukwatwa oburwaire bwanyima y'okuzaara aha omu Uganda, harimu obutagasi bwingi, okushaasha omutwe, n'okuzimba omubiri. Okuzibira nikubaasa kuhikwaho orikukoresa omubazi gwona ogurikuhebwa omushaho, okurinda obuyonjo, n'okurya ebyokurya ebirikubaasa kuhwera abasirikare b'omubiri. (ebigambo 46)",
            "Ku oraabe otarikubaasa kuhuumura kurungi ahabw'obujunaanizibwa bw'eka yaawe, noobaasa kukikora orikunywa amaizi maingi n'okukora emirimo y'omuka oshutami, okukyendeeza aha buremeezi bw'omubiri gwawe.",
            "Ku oraabe noogumizamu kujwa eshagama bwanyima y'okuzaara aha omu Uganda, oshemereire kunywa amaizi,  obushera n'amaizi garimu omwonyo, okwetantara okuteerana, esande mukaaga kuruga aha kuzaara zitakahikire, n'okuza omu eirwariro erikuri haihi, obumanyiso ku burikugumaho.",
            "Noobaasa kureebuuza oku orikutereera omuka omu Uganda otaine kukyeberwa omu eirwariro orikureeba waaba orikureta eshagama kuruga omu bukazi orikureebera aha paadi, orikureeba yaaba oine okuzimba omu bicweka by'ahansi, n'okwetantara okuteerana omu sande mukaaga ez'okubanza, kugira ngu obukazi na  nyin'enda  bibanze byatereera.",
            "Eego, hariho emibazi y'omubyaro erikubaasa kuhwera abakazi abamazire kuzaara omuri Uganda, nk'okukora ebisasaizi nka Kegel, okukwata enkari waaba noosheesha, n'okunaaba obwire n'amaizi garikutagata garimu omwonyo buri hahwaho akaire kakye.",
            "Ku oraabe oine oburemeezi bw'okwonsa kandi otarikubaasa kutunga obuhwezi bw'okwonsa omu Uganda, oshemereire kugambira omushaho ori haihi, okukira munonga waaba oine okuzimba kw'amabeere nainga obumanyiso obundi oburikukwata aha kwonsya.",
            "Okukora aha mpindahinduka y'oburemeezi bw'omukazi ahanyima y'okuzaara n'obuhabuzi bukye kuruga omu bashaho omu Uganda, nikitwariramu okwetegyereza ngu buriijo nikibaho ahabw'empindahinduka y'omubiri. Okweyongyera kw'oburemeezi, okukoresa emiringo etari emwe, okurya ebyokurya ebirimu ebiriisa bikye hamwe n'amaizi garikutagata, nikibaasa kuhwera. Okukyendeeza oburemeezi, ta omutima aha by'okurya ebirimu ebiriisa byona, okubyama ekirikumara, n'okuronda obuhwezi kureeberera oburemeezi.",
            "Enkora nungi y'okurinda obuyonjo bw'omubiri bwanyima y'okuzaara omuri Yuganda, erimu okuhindura paadi obutoosha, okukoresa emyenda ya pamba, okukira munonga eyomunda, okunaaba emirundi ebiri buri izooba, okukoresa esabuuni okwozya  emyenda, n'okurinda obuyonjo bw'omwana okurwanisa oburwaire.",
            "Ku oraabe noohurira okuremererwa kandi otarikubaasa kuhika aha muhabuzi w'eby'omutwe omu Uganda, gyezaho kugamba n'omuntu ou orikwesiga, nk'omuntu w'omuka yaawe nainga munywani waawe ow'ahamara, kandi oyeikirize kugamba ebirikukwerarikiriza n'enyehurira zaawe.",
            "Ku oraabe oine oburemeezi bw'amaani bw'okwerarikirira nainga okwerarikirira bwanyima y'okuzaara omu Uganda, n'eky'omugasho kusherura obuhwezi kuruga aha muhabuzi nainga omushaho ahonaaho nk'oku kirikubaasika, ahabw'okuba nabaasa kukuha obuhabuzi n'obuhwezi obu orikwetenga.",
            "Okukora aha bubonero oburikukira kureebeka ahanyima y'okuzaara nk'okutuutuka n'okufukirirwa nyekiro omu Uganda, nikihaburwa okwetantara okunywa ebirikwotsya n'okujwara ebijwaro bya pamba, ahabw'okuba ebi nibibaasa kuhwera omu kureeberera obutagatsi bw'omubiri n'okureetaho obusingye.",
            "Eego, hariho eby'okwegyezamu ebirikwetengwa ahabw'okugaruka omu mbeera yaawe bwanyima y'okuzaara ebi orikubaasa kukorera omuka omu Uganda, nk'okutambura mporampora n'okukora ebisasaizi bya Kegel, kugira ngu oyongyere okuguma kw'enyama za matako.",
            "Okureeba ngu habaho eby'okurya ebirikumara omu Uganda, noobaasa kugura eby'okurya by'omuhendo gw'ahansi kandi ebirimu ebiriisa kuruga omu butare bw'omubyaro. Okwongyera ahari ekyo, okukoresa omusiri mukye kuhinga emboga nikibaasa kureetaho eby'okurya ebiine ebirrisa ebirikwetengwa.",
            "Obubonero oburikworeka ngu oshemereire kuronda obujanjabi ahonaaho bwanyima y'okuzaara omuri Uganda, harimu okurwara munonga omutwe, okurwara ekyaata, okushaasha kw'ekifuba, okushaasha kw'omunda-nto, nainga okurugwa omubukazi amaizi gari kunuka, ahabw'okuba ebi nibibaasa kworeka oburemeezi.",
            "Ku oraabe otarikubaasa kuza omu eirwariro ahabw'oburemeezi bwanyima y'okuzaara omu Uganda, noobaasa kugumiraho orikuhamya ngu nohuumura ekirikumara, orikusherura obuhwezi n'obuhwezi kuruga omu banywani baawe n'abanyabuzaare baawe.",
            "Eego, hariho emicwe y'obuhangwa omuri Uganda erikubaasa kuhwera omukukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, nk'okukoresa emibazi y'eby'obuhangwa hamwe n'okukoresa ebintu ebirikuba biriho omwihanga, ebirikugabirwa abazaire n'abazaire.",
            "Ku oraabe oine oburemeezi kandi otarikubaasa kuza omu eirwariro omuri Uganda, oshemereire kumanyisa ab'eby'amagara omu kyaro kyawe nainga okuteera esimu abanywani baawe nainga abanyabuzaare baawe kutunga obuhwezi. Omu bwire bw'akabi munonga, noobaasa kugambaho n'omushaho, okutunga obuhabuzi.",
            "Enyikiriza n'emitwarize y'abantu b'omu kyanga kyangye omu Uganda nibitwariramu ekigyendererwa ngu abakazi bashemereire kugurira abaana baabo (abatakazairwe)  ebintu, n'okukoresa emibazi y'eby'obuhangwa erikukira kuhebwa abazaarisa.",
            "Ngaaha, nyowe nk'omuntu tindikukuratira engyenderwaho y'eby'obuhangwa n'enyikiriza omu Uganda. Enkora yangye neekira kwegamira aha kumanya kw'abantu boona hamwe n'ebi ndikukunda okukira okukuratira eby'obuhangwa.",
            "Nimpurira gye ahabw'okuba maama aha omu Uganda. Okwerarikirira oku mbaire nyine nikukwatagana n'obutagasi bwingi bw'omubiri gw'omwana wangye bwanyima y'okugyemesa, kwonka eky'omugisha, ebyo bukahwaho.",
            "Ngaaha, tinyine ki ndikwenda kwebuuza aha magara gangye omu Uganda.",
            "Ahabw'okushemererwa aha omu Uganda, ninkunda kureeba firimu, okugamba na banywani bangye, n'okuza omu kanisa. Ebintu ebi nibimpwera okuhuumura n'okuhurira nyine akakwate.",
            "Aha omu Uganda, ninyegyendesereza oburemeezi obwo ndikugamba n'omuntu ou ndikwesiga, nk'abanywani bangye ab'ahamara. Okubagambira oku ndikwehurira nikimpwera kugumira oburemeezi bwona.",
            "Eego,ninkoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa, nk'okukoresa emibazi y'ebishaka omu kuzaara, ekirikwikirizibwa ngu nikihwera omu kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara.",
            "Eego, ntungire omukago murungi n'omwana wangye omuri Uganda, kandi nimpurira gye. Omukago ogu nigundeetera okushemererwa kwingi.",
            "Ngaaha, tihaine eki ndikwenda kwebuuza aha magara gangye obwahati. Nimpurira gye.",
            "Hurira ngu hariho empindahinduka omu rangi y'omubiri. Ningyezaho kunaaba burizooba.",
            "Ku oraabe otarikubaasa kutunga obujanjabi bw'obusaasi bwanyima y'okuzaara, yenyige n'ekintu kiri kufukirira aha myanya erikukwatwaho nikibaasa kuhwera omu kukyendeeza obusaasi. Nyigaho mporampora kumara obwire bukye emirundi mingi omu eizooba.",
            "Ku oraabe oine oburemeezi bw'okukira kuruga omu kushemezibwa kandi hatariho by'okukoresa, n'eky'omugasho kugaruka omu eirwariro ahu waabaire nokyebererwa n'okuragurirwa.",
            "Ku oraabe otari haihi n'eirwariro kandi orikwetenga okureeberera ehuuzi n'ekironda bwanyima y'okuzaara, oshemereire kuyonja gye omwanya ogwe n'amaizi g'omwonyo mukye, okuzibira okukwatwa obukooko.",
            "Obubonero bw'okukwatwa obukooko bwanyima y'okuzaara, harimu omushwija gw'amaani hamwe n'okuhumura kubi (okunuuka). Okukizibira nikitwariramu okunywa emibazi nk'oku erikworekwa, okurinda obuyonjo, n'okureeba ngu n'ohuumura ekirikumara orikushaba ab'omuka yaawe okuhwera omu kukureeberera.",
            "Ku oraabe otarikubaasa kuhuumura ekirikumara omu bwire bw'okutereera ahabw'obujunaanizibwa bw'eka yaawe, nikihaburwa kuza omwirwariro nainga ow'omushaho kutunga obuhabuzi aha ku orikubaasa kukora eki kurungi.",
            "Ku oraagumizemu kujwa eshagama bwanyima y'okuzaara, oshemereire kuronda obujanjabi ahonaaho. N'obu okukira omubiri n'ebiteekateeko ky'omugasho, okuruga eshagamamu nikwetenga okushwijumwa omukugu w'e by'amagara.",
            "Nikibaasa kuguma munonga okukuratirira oku orikutereera omuka otaine kukyeberwa buri kaire. Ku oraabe oine ebikwerarikiriza, nikirungi okuronda obuhabuzi kuruga aha bashaho waaba nikibaasika.",
            "Eego, emibazi y'omubyaro erikubaasa kuhwera omu kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, neetwariramu okureeberera eby'okurya byawe obwo orikurya emboga nyingi, ezirikwetengwa omukureeta ebiriisa ebirikwetengwa omu kukira.",
            "Ku oraabe oine oburemeezi bw'okwonsa kandi otarikubaasa kutunga obuhwezi, okuhaburwa okuheirwe aha nikureebeka kuba nikukwata aha kureeberera oburemeezi. Aha nshonga z'okwonsa, okuronda obuhwezi kuruga aha bashaho nikihaburwa.",
            "Obuhabuzi obuheirwe aha, okunaaba omungaro n'okuboneza omubiri, nibukwata aha buyonjo, kutari kukora aha mpindahinduka y'oburemeezi bw'omubiri bwanyima y'okuzaara. Kubaasa kukyendeera nainga kwongyera aha mubiri, ni kirungi kwebuuza aha bashaho kyaaba nikibaasika.",
            "Ekiteiso ky'okukora ebisasayizi kwenda kwebwa tikirikukwata butunu aha kukuuma obuyonjo bw'omuntu. Enkora nungi erimu okunaaba, okuhindura paadi buri kaire, n'okujwara emyenda erikwera, okuzibira okujanjaara kw'oburwaire.",
            "Ku oraabe nohurira oburemeezi bwingi kandi otarikubaasa kuhika aha muhabuzi w'eby'omutwe, okugamba n'omushaho omu irwariro ryawe, nikibaasa kukuha obuhwezi n'obuhabuzi aha by'okukoresa ebiriho.",
            "Okwenyiga n'ekirika, ti muringo gw'okuragurira obuuremeezi nainga okwerarikirira kw'amaani bwanyima y'okuzaara. Ku oraabe oine oburemeezi obu, n'eky'omugasho kusherura obuhwezi kuruga aha bakugu b'ebyamagara ahonaaho.",
            "Okugira ngu eego tikirikushoboorora oku orikubaasa kurwanisa okugira ekyooya nainga embeho nyekiro. Omuringo gw'okuhweeraho nigubaasa kutwariramu okujwara ebijwaro ebirikurabamu embeho, okuguma noonywa amaizi, n'okuhindura obutagatsi bw'ekishengye. Ku oraabe oine oburemeezi bw'amaani, reeba omushaho aho naaho.",
            "Okurya eby'okurya birungi, ebijuma n'emboga hamwe n'okuguma oine amaizi omumubiri n'eby'omugasho ahabw'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara, kwonka n'ebisasaizi by'omutaano nk'okutambura hamwe n'okukora Kegels nabyo nbihigibwa okuhwera omubiri kugarukamu.",
            "Eky'okugarukamu okurujwa eshagama y'amaani tikirikushoboorora oku omuntu arikubaasa kurya kurungi n'eby'okurya bikye. Okwebembeza ebyokurya ebyokurya ebirimu ebiriisa n'okushaba obuhabuzi kuruga omu bashaho n'abantu b'omubyaro nikibaasa kuhwera.",
            "Okugira ngu ngaaha kwonka tikikihikire. Hariho obubonero oburikwetenga okuragurirwa ahonaaho, nk'okujwa eshagama nyingi, omushwija mwingi, obusaasi bw'amaani, nainga oburemeezi omu kwisya.",
            "Ku oraabe otarikubaasa kuza omu irwariro ry'eby'amagara ahabw'oburemeezi bwanyima y'okuzaara, okuronda obuhwezi kuruga owa tiimu y'eby'amagara omubyaro omu kyanga kyawe, nikibaasa kukuha obuhabuzi n'obuhwezi.",
            "Eky'okugarukamu nikyoreka enyikiriza y'okugyema hamwe n'enyikiriza y'eby'okurya, ebirikukwata aha magara, kwonka tikirikumanyisa enkora y'obuhangwa ey'okukira bwanyima y'okuzaara. Eby'obuhangwa nibibaasa kuba birimu emibazi y'ebishaka nainga emikoro etari emwe.",
            "Eky'okugarukamu Eego - ekyo n'enyikiriza y'okugyema tikirikugamba butunu eki oshemereire kukora waaba oine oburemeezi kandi otarikubaasa kutambura. Omu mbeera nk'ezo, okuronda obuhwezi kuruga omu bashaho b'omubyaro, nikyo ky'okubanza.",
            "Okushemererwa ahabw'okuba maama hamwe n'okukunda abaana, n'ekiteekateeko ky'omuntu buntu, tikirikumanyisa enzikiriza n'emitwarize omu bantu ebirikukwata aha magara n'okukira.",
            "Ebyarugiremu nibyoreka ngu okuhika aha irwariro, nikibaasa kuba kigumire, ekirikworeka oburemeezi oburikukwata aha kuhisya obuheereza bw'eby'amagara, kitari kikorwa ky'obuhangwa nainga enyikiriza erikukuratirwa.",
            "Okugarukwamu nikugamba aha kutaayaayira abanywani n'okugira obwire bw'okuhuumura, ekirikukwata aha kuba gye kwonka tikirikugarukamu butunu ebikwatiraine n'obuzaire nainga okwerarikirira kwona.",
            "Okugarukwamu nikushoboorora okurwanisa oburemeezi obwo orikubagana ebirikukwata aha magara gaawe, kitari kubuuza nainga okwerarikirira aha magara gaawe.",
            "Ekigambo ngaaha nikyoreka ngu omuntu taine bwire bw'okuhuumura nainga okwejumba omu mirimo y'okushemererwa, ekirikukwata aha magara gye omu bwire bw'okukira.",
            "Eky'okugarukamu Ninyehurira gye buriijo kandi nshemereirwe nikyoreka emiteekateekyere mirungi kwonka tikirikushoboorora oburyo bw'okureeberera oburemeezi nainga haaba hariho omuntu ou arikubaasa kugamba nawe.",
            "Eky'okugarukamu kirungi nikibaasa kuba nikimanyisa okuhurira gye. Okugamba aha kukoresa omubiri, okurya kurungi, hamwe n'okukyeberwa omu irwariro, nikyoreka emiringo y'okwerinda kwonka tikirikugamba butunu aha kukwatanisa.",
            "Eego, hariho emiringo y'okuzaara ey'obuhangwa eshemereire kwetantarwa, okureeba ngu wazaara kurungi. N'eky'omugasho okuhanuura n'omushaho, okwetegyereza emize erikubaasa kuba ey'akabi aha magara gaawe.",
            "Okukoresa emiringo y'obuhangwa hamwe n'obuhabuzi bw'eby'amagara obw'omurembe omu bwire bw'enda, nikitwariramu abakugu omu by'amagara okukyebera amagara g'abakazi  hamwe n'okuheereza amaka obwegyese oburikukwata aha magara gaabo.",
            "Ekigarukamu ekyoroobi eego nikyoreeyoreka ngu hariho enyikiriza z'obuhangwa ezikukwata aha kutwara enda n'okuzaara omu bantu, kwonka terikworeka butunu enzikiriza ezo.",
            "ab'eby'amagara, okushomesa abakazi aha kabi akari omu mitwarize y'obuhangwa omu kuzaara",
            "Okuferwa omumwa gwa nyinenda, ahabw'okukoresa n'omuringo gw'okurahusa okuzaara, obwo orikukoresa emibazi y'obuhangwa",
            "Okwegyesa munonga abakazi n'abashaija abazaire",
            "Eego, hariho enteekateeka za gavumenti hamwe n'ebitongore ebitari bya Gavumenti omu Uganda ebirikuhwera abakazi b'enda. Noobaasa kubuuza ah'eirwariro ry'omukyanga kyawe nainga amarwariro g'omubyaro ebirikukwata aha puroguraamu eziriho.",
            "Kurabira omu kutaho ebiragiro by'okukuratira n'okureeba ngu buri mushaho w'eby'obuhangwa aine raisensi",
            "Okuheereza abakazi emibazi y'ebishaka, nikibahwera kurahusyaho aha bw'okuzaara.",
            "okworeka eka yangye akabi akarikubaasa kuruga omu kukoresa emize y'enzaarwa.",
            "Eego, hariho emibazi y'enzaarwa erikukoresibwa omu bwire bw'okutwara enda omu Uganda, kwonka n'eky'omugasho kumanya egyo etaine kabi hamwe n'egyo eshemereire kwetantarwa. Nikirungi kwebuuza aha bashaho, okutunga obuhabuzi aha nshonga egi.",
