            "Ku orasharemu kukuratira obuhabuzi bw'eby'amagara obwa hati omu Uganda, noobaasa kusherura obuhwezi kuruga omu bantu b'omukyanga kyawe, obwo orikubahiga kukoresa amarwariro g'omurembe, n'okugabana amakuru agarikukwata aha migasho y'eby'amagara g'abakazi abaine enda n'abaana baabo.",
            "Enyikiriza y'obuhangwa erikukwata aha kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara omuri Yuganda, erimu emiringo y'okukora ebisasaizi n'okushutama omu mibazi y'obuhangwa. Ebi nibibaasa kukwatanisibwa n'obuhabuzi bw'abashaho, okureeba ngu eby'okukoresa nibibaasa kuhwera abakazi abamazire kuzaara, hamwe n'okuhanuura n'abashaho aha bikwatireine n'okukoresa eby'obuhangwa.",
