            "1. Okushutama omu mibazi y'ebishaka, noobaasa kuzaara gye. Ku orikurya eitaka nainga eibumba, nibiija kutuma wazaara omwana oine amagara marungi",
            "Okwegyesa ebikwatireine n'eby'amagara n'okuguma nooza omu eirwariro kukyebeza enda, okutazaarira omuka.",
