            "Eby'okurya eby'omugasho: 1. Yongyera abazaire amaani okunywa obushera bw'oburo n'okurya oburo okwongyera ekiriisa kya iron omu mubiri, n'emboga. 2. abazaire bagume (nibanywa amaizi) baine amaizi maingi omu mibiri yaabo. Enkora y'akabi: 1. Okwetantara okurya enyama n'amahuri, nikibaasa kurugwamu oburemeezi bw'omubiri kuburwa ebyougombeka 2. Okurya eby'okurya bigumire kandi byomire baaba bari haihi kuzaara, nikibareetera okugumirwa. Okwetantara kurya nikibareetera enjara erikuhika aha bwire bw'okuzaara obu barikuremwa kusindika omwana 4. Abamwe tibarikurya kandi omu mwanya gw'ekyo nibaheebwa emibazi y'ebishaka, ekirikureetera nyina n'omwana kurya kubi.",
