            "Okutunga oburinganiza ahagati y'emitwarize y'obuhangwa n'ey'omurembe ahabw'okuzaara omu Uganda, nikitwariramu okukoresa emikoro y'obuhangwa n'emigyenzo y'omurembe omu bwire bw'okuzaara omu marwariro.",
            "Eby'obuhangwa ebikwatiraine n'okureeberera abakazi ahanyima y'okuzaara omu Uganda, nibitwariramu okurya eby'okurya ebimwe ebirikuteekateekwaho kuba nibihwera omu kukira. Ebi nibibaasa kukoresibwa kurungi, okureeba ngu biine ebiriisa kandi byongyera aha buhabuzi bw'abashaho.",
