            "Ku orikucwamu kukuratira obuhabuzi bw'eby'amagara obwa hati omu Uganda, noobaasa kusherura obuhwezi kuruga omu bantu b'omukyanga kyawe, obwo orikubahiga kukoresa obuheereza bw'amarwariro, n'okugabana amakuru agarikukwata aha migasho yokuzariira omw'eirwariro aha amagara g'omuzaire n'omwana.",
            "Enyikiriza y'obuhangwa erikukwata aha kukira bwanyima y'okuzaara omu Uganda, neetwariramu okukoresa emiringo y'eby'emizaano. Ebi nibibaasa kukwatanisibwa n'ebiragiro by'abashaho, okureeba ngu eby'okukoresa nibirungi kandi tibirikwerarikiriza ahanyima y'okuzaara, nk'oku kirikuhaburwa abakugu omu by'amagara.",
