            "Nobu eirwariro ryawe ryaba riri hare n'eka yaawe omuri Yuganda, nikihaburwa kuza kukyebeza enda emirundi ena, n'obu kiraabe kiri kirungi, omuhendo gw'okukyebeza  enda n'emirundi munaana niyo bashemereire kuza omu irwariro kukyebeza enda.",
            "Omu byaro bya Uganda, obuheereza bw'eby'amagara g'abakazi abaine enda obwa busha n'obw'esente nkye nibutwariramu okutayayira tiimu z'abebyamagara z'ebyaro, ezirikubaasa kuheereza obuheereza bukuru n'okukugaita aha marwariro agahikire.",
            "Ku oraabe otarikubaasa kushashurira okukyebera n'emibazi omu bwire obu otwaire enda omu Uganda, oshemereire kutayayira eirwariro rya gavumenti erikuri haihi, ahabw'okuba nirikuheereza obuheereza bw'eby'amagara oburi ahansi munonga.",
